0fleeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.oxfordmartin.ox.ac.uk%2Fdownloads%2Facademic%2FThe_Future_of_Employment.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EFrey%20and%20Oscbone's%20widely%20cited%20study%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%2047%25%20of%20jobs%20in%20the%20United%20States%20are%20at%20risk%20of%20being%20automated.%20Customer%20service%20agents%20are%20at%20risk%20from%20chat%20bots%2C%20and%20even%20highly%20specialized%20and%20well-compensated%20jobs%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-jobs-at-risk-replacement-artificial-intelligence-ai-labor-trends-2023-02%23traders-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EWall%20Street%20traders%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20not%20immune%20to%20big%20change.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20even%20if%20you%20find%20yourself%20in%20the%20remaining%2053%25%2C%20the%20skills%20and%20experiences%20required%20in%20your%20job%20will%20change%20quickly%2C%20repeatedly%20and%20frequently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdvice%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESubstantially%20increase%20time%20and%20distance%20away%20from%20your%20comfort-zone.%20For%20example%2C%20put%20together%20a%20slide%20deck%20with%20your%20point%20of%20view%20on%20how%20your%20current%20job%20will%20evolve%20over%20the%20next%20three%20years%20and%20present%20it%20to%20as%20many%20people%20that%20will%20listen.%20Be%20bold%20and%20seek%20feedback%20from%20a%20diverse%20group%20of%20stakeholders.%20Exchanging%20thoughts%20with%20new%20people%20and%20testing%20your%20ideas%20mentally%20prepares%20you%20to%20anticipate%20and%20adapt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Reinforce%20the%20human-touch%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIronically%2C%20as%20AI%20proliferates%20around%20us%2C%20the%20characteristics%20that%20make%20us%20human%20become%20more%20important%2C%20not%20less.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGenAI%20will%20undoubtedly%20boost%20your%20productivity%2C%20but%20it%20also%20makes%20everyone%20else%20better%20as%20well.%20If%20your%20competitors%20can%20quickly%20answer%20nuanced%20questions%20and%20author%20insightful%20reports%20as%20well%20as%20you%20can%2C%20how%20do%20you%20stand%20out%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20keep%20advancing%20your%20career%2C%20capitalize%20on%20the%20serendipity%20of%20human%20interaction%20that%20machines%20cannot%20emulate.%20Put%20a%20heavier%20emphasis%20on%20perfecting%20in-person%20human%20interaction%20and%20find%20ways%20to%20differentiate%20yourself%20in%20the%20real-world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdvice%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Practice%20public%20speaking%20and%20attend%20conferences.%20Build%20your%20network%20and%20your%20brand.%20Try%20solving%20novel%20problems%20and%20work%20on%20articulating%20your%20ideas%20to%20audiences%20big%20and%20small.%20For%20example%2C%20do%20something%20uncomfortable%20like%20attending%20in-person%20meet%20ups%20on%20a%20subject%20you%20know%20nothing%20about.%20Periodically%2C%20do%20it%20again%20on%20another%20subject%20where%20you%20have%20zero%20expertise.%20Socialize%20and%20make%20new%20friends%20at%20these%20events%20to%20expand%20your%20knowledge%20network.%20Put%20yourself%20out%20there%20and%20put%20in%20the%20effort%20to%20be%20different%20in%20the%20analog%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Be%20humble%20and%20constantly%20re-tool%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGoing%20forward%2C%20seemingly%20prestigious%20career%20prospects%20can%20turn%20into%20a%20chaotic%20string%20of%20job%20hopping%20if%20you%20don't%20have%20the%20humility%20and%20awareness%20to%20constantly%20re-tool.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20many%20bumps%2C%20turns%2C%20and%20forks%20you%20experience%20while%20navigating%20your%20career%20will%20become%20ever%20steeper%20and%20sharper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20must%20constantly%20earn%20the%20right%20to%20be%20successful.%20Just%20because%20you%20%3Cem%3Ewere%3C%2Fem%3E%20successful%20doesn't%20mean%20you%20%3Cem%3Ewill%3C%2Fem%3E%20be%20successful%2C%20even%20in%20the%20same%20field.%20The%20skills%20you%20need%20to%20maneuver%20a%20career%20will%20constantly%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdvice%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Take%20classes%20that%20your%20peers%20aren't%20taking%20and%20read%20books%20that%20your%20competitors%20aren't%20reading.%20For%20a%20highly%20technical%20person%2C%20this%20could%20mean%20doing%20something%20uncomfortable%20like%20taking%20an%20online%20course%20on%20the%20history%20of%20Renaissance%20art.%20Stretching%20your%20mind%20in%20unique%20ways%20prevents%20you%20from%20the%20trap%20of%20thinking%20%26quot%3Bthis%20would%20never%20work%26quot%3B%20when%20you%20come%20across%20new%20ideas%20in%20your%20space.%20Don't%20extrapolate%20past%20success.%20Prepare%20your%20mind%20to%20constantly%20look%20at%20things%20from%20new%20perspectives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20winning%20mentality%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20new%20paradigm%20for%20careers%20may%20seem%20daunting%2C%20the%20next%20decade%20could%20be%20the%20most%20prosperous%20decade%20in%20human%20history.%20AI%20and%20GenAI%20could%20add%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pwc.com%2Fgx%2Fen%2Fissues%2Fdata-and-analytics%2Fpublications%2Fartificial-intelligence-study.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cu%3Etens%20of%20trillions%20of%20dollars%20to%20the%20world%20economy%2C%20boost%20productivity%20and%20supercharge%20innovation.%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHard%20skills%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20important%2C%20but%20perfecting%20your%20soft%20skills%20in%20the%20analog%20world%20will%20serve%20as%20the%20enduring%20north%20star%20that%20guides%20you%20towards%20successful%20outcomes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimply%20put%2C%20hard%20skills%20can%20make%20you%20good%20at%20one%20job%2C%20while%20soft%20skills%20can%20make%20you%20good%20at%20%3Cem%3Emany%3C%2Fem%3E%20jobs.%20Those%20that%20build%20upon%20their%20soft%20skills%20to%20constantly%20adapt%2C%20reset%20and%20reinvent%20will%20thrive%20in%20the%20Age%20of%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EJunta%20Nakai%20is%20a%20global%20vice%20president%20and%20head%20of%20financial%20services%2C%20cybersecurity%20and%20sustainability%20at%20Databricks.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcareer-growth-most-important-soft-skills-ai-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697707921000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653051ef96f7540cd05ffd44%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcareer-growth-most-important-soft-skills-ai-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mindset%20changes%20will%20help%20your%20career%20thrive%20as%20AI%20becomes%20more%20ubiquitous.%20Focus%20on%20soft%20skills%20and%20meaningful%20personal%20interactions%20with%20others.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Junta%20Nakai)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcareer-growth-most-important-soft-skills-ai-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Merchant%20of%20Venice%E2%80%99%20U.K.%20Production%20Ups%20Security%20in%20Wake%20of%20Hamas%20Attacks%3A%20%E2%80%98It%E2%80%99s%20Like%20a%20Dystopian%20Nightmare%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697707881000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FThe-Merchant-of-Venice-1936.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235761713%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20touring%20production%20of%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Merchant%20of%20Venice%201936%E2%80%9D%20has%20been%20targeted%20by%20antisemites%2C%20its%20star%20revealed.%20Tracy-Ann%20Oberman%2C%20who%20has%20starred%20in%20%E2%80%9CDoctor%20Who%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9CFriday%20Night%20Dinner%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20tour%20of%20the%20Shakespearean%20