It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20first%20graduated%20from%20college%2C%20I%20knew%20I%20wanted%20to%20do%20two%20main%20things%3A%20travel%20and%20work%20remotely.%20Initially%2C%20I%20didn't%20see%20myself%20as%20a%20digital%20nomad%2C%20but%20the%20more%20I%20traveled%20while%20working%2C%20the%20more%20accurate%20it%20seemed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202022%20when%20I%20lived%20as%20a%20nomad%2C%20I%20went%20to%20the%20UK%2C%20France%2C%20Switzerland%2C%20Italy%2C%20Spain%2C%20New%20York%2C%20California%20and%20Japan.%20I%20worked%20as%20a%20freelance%20video%20editor%20during%20this%20time%2C%20and%20only%20needed%20a%20computer%20and%20internet%20connection.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20that%20year%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20leave%20the%20nomadic%20lifestyle%20behind%20and%20live%20in%20New%20York%20City%20permanently.%20While%20working%20as%20a%20digital%20nomad%20had%20many%20perks%20%E2%80%94%20and%20although%20it%20was%20once%20my%20dream%20%E2%80%94%20I%20learned%20there%20are%20some%20drawbacks%20to%20this%20lifestyle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E1.%20It%20was%20hard%20managing%20my%20spending%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20freelancer%2C%20my%20income%20is%20already%20unstable.%20When%20I%20was%20traveling%2C%20the%20amount%20of%20money%20I%20spent%20varied%20from%20place%20to%20place.%20For%20example%2C%20when%20I%20was%20in%20Bali%2C%20my%20money%20stretched%20a%20bit%20further%20than%20it%20did%20in%20America.%20But%20when%20I%20was%20in%20Japan%2C%20I%20had%20to%20budget%20my%20money%20carefully.%20I%20knew%20I%20had%20fixed%20expenses%20like%20food%2C%20transportation%2C%20and%20accommodations%20like%20my%20Airbnb%2C%20but%20I%20never%20knew%20how%20much%20I%20would%20actually%20be%20spending%20until%20I%20got%20to%20a%20certain%20location.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20finances%20fluctuated%20because%20each%20country%20was%20so%20different%2C%20and%20I%20also%20wasn't%20the%20best%20at%20budgeting.%20Since%20it%20was%20my%20first%20time%20traveling%20abroad%2C%20there%20was%20a%20big%20learning%20curve%2C%20especially%20surrounding%20money%20and%20knowing%20how%20much%20I%20could%20spend.%20Traveling%20abroad%20was%20new%20to%20me%2C%20and%20while%20managing%20my%20money%20in%20foreign%20countries%20was%20hard%2C%20I%20learned%20a%20lot%20from%20the%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bhandari%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6529966755f52b01b35f75d8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBhandari%20went%20to%20Italy%2C%20Spain%2C%20New%20York%20and%20more%20living%20her%20dream%20as%20a%20nomad.%3Cp%3ECelina%20Bhandari%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E2.%20I%20had%20a%20hard%20time%20maintaining%20friendships%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20met%20so%20many%20people%20when%20I%20was%20a%20digital%20nomad%2C%20but%20because%20I%20was%20always%20moving%2C%20the%20people%20I%20met%20couldn't%20be%20consistent%20friends.%20I'd%20make%20friends%2C%20but%20when%20I'd%20leave%20for%20another%20country%20or%20place%2C%20those%20friendships%20became%20harder%20to%20maintain.%20Using%20social%20media%20to%20stay%20in%20contact%20helps%20a%20bit%2C%20but%20it's%20hard%20to%20feel%20close%20when%20you're%20no%20longer%20in%20the%20same%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERomantic%20relationships%20were%20the%20same%20way.%20Although%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20in%20a%20relationship%2C%20it%20felt%20too%20hard%20to%20maintain%20one%20when%20traveling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20came%20to%20my%20friends%20back%20home%2C%20it%20felt%20a%20bit%20harder%20to%20relate%20to%20them%2C%20and%20I%20realized%20we%20were%20on%20different%20wavelengths.%20Many%20of%20my%20friends%20were%20starting%209-to-5%20jobs%20and%20working%20full-time%2C%20but%20I%20was%20focused%20on%20traveling%2C%20which%20was%20unrelatable%20to%20them.%20I%20definitely%20got%20lonely%20at%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20a%20big%20reason%20why%20I%20stopped%20being%20a%20digital%20nomad%20%E2%80%94%20I%20wanted%20to%20have%20a%20consistent%20community%20of%20people%20in%20my%20life.%20Now%20that%20I%20live%20in%20one%20place%2C%20it%20has%20become%20easier%20to%20maintain%20long-lasting%20friendships.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Celina%20Bhandari%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6529871f6561dd877e7a623e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223006%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EShe%20found%20it%20hard%20to%20maintain%20relationships%20while%20constantly%20traveling.%3Cp%3ECelina%20Bhandari%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E3.%20Building%20a%20consistent%20routine%20felt%20challenging%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20big%20challenge%20for%20me%20was%20a%20lack%20of%20routine.%20When%20you're%20constantly%20moving%2C%20it's%20hard%20to%20maintain%20and%20develop%20healthy%20habits%20and%20routines.%20Something%20like%20waking%20up%20at%20the%20same%20time%20or%20going%20to%20the%20gym%20felt%20harder.%20As%20much%20as%20I%20enjoy%20going%20to%20the%20gym%2C%20I%20never%20wanted%20to%20get%20a%20membership%20when%20I%20knew%20I'd%20be%20moving%20again%20in%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20that%20said%2C%20I've%20always%20found%20routines%20and%20habits%20to%20be%20important%2C%20especially%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20work.%20Although%20I%20wanted%20to%20advance%20myself%20in%20my%20career%2C%20not%20having%20a%20stable%20routine%20and%20even%20a%20consistent%20time%20zone%20felt%20challenging.%20Since%20my%20clients%20were%20based%20in%20the%20US%2C%20I%20was%20constantly%20trying%20to%20figure%20out%20the%20right%20time%20to%20take%20phone%20calls%20and%20meetings%20that%20wasn't%20at%20midnight%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222047%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Celina%20Bhandari%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6529875b6561dd