d%20adding%20hot%20tubs%20and%20thinking%20of%20the%20cover%20image%20had%20given%20her%20Airbnbs%20an%20edge.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Jamie%20Inlow%2C%2032%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bestillgetaways.com%2Fstays%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBe%20Still%20Getaways%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%20Insider%20has%20verified%20Inow's%20earnings%20and%20listings.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20loved%20the%20idea%20of%20running%20an%20Airbnb.%20But%20it%20wasn't%20until%20my%20family%20moved%20to%20Scottsville%2C%20Virginia%2C%20in%202019%20that%20I%20had%20the%20opportunity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20working%20as%20a%20program%20director%20for%20Appalachian%20State%20University%20but%20wanted%20a%20better%20work-life%20balance%20to%20spend%20time%20with%20my%20son.%20I%20thought%20Airbnb%20would%20give%20me%20that%20flexibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMy%20neighbor's%20sheep%20barn%20was%20a%20golden%20opportunity%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20neighbor%20in%20Scottsville%20owned%20a%20sheep%20farm.%20In%20June%202019%2C%20he%20showed%20me%20his%20barn%20with%20an%20apartment%20above%20that%20was%20standing%20empty.%20The%20farmer%20and%20his%20family%20had%20a%20busy%20life%20and%20no%20time%20to%20do%20anything%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20saw%20the%20apartment%2C%20I%20went%20home%20that%20night%20and%20wrote%20a%20business%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20proposed%20that%20my%20neighbor%20give%20me%20%242%2C000%20to%20furnish%20the%20apartment%20and%20rent%20it%20on%20Airbnb.%20I'd%20manage%20it%20and%20we%20could%20split%20the%20profits.%20The%20following%20day%2C%20he%20left%20an%20envelope%20of%20money%20on%20my%20front%20porch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Be%20Still%20Getaways%20luxury%20apartment%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%2