ht%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20property%20Inlow%20manages%20in%20Charlottesville%2C%20Virginia.%3Cp%3EBe%20Still%20Getaways%20luxury%20apartment%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EFacebook%20helped%20me%20expand%20my%20portfolio%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20posted%20on%20Facebook%20about%20my%20brand%20called%20%26quot%3BBe%20Still%20Getaways.%26quot%3B%20One%20of%20my%20old%20school%20friends%20messaged%20me%20to%20say%20she'd%20just%20bought%20two%20buildings%20in%20downtown%20Staunton%2C%20Virginia%2C%20and%20needed%20someone%20to%20manage%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20doing%20everything%20on%20my%20own%20for%20about%20a%20year%20%E2%80%94%20working%20as%20an%20educational%20consultant%2C%20cleaning%20the%20Airbnbs%2C%20and%20looking%20after%20my%20son.%20I%20was%20burning%20the%20candle%20at%20both%20ends.%20But%20I%20couldn't%20leave%20my%20job%20as%20an%20educational%20consultant%2C%20as%20we%20also%20had%20taken%20out%20a%20loan%20on%20a%20new%20home%20for%20the%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20late%202020%2C%20the%20business%20took%20a%20real%20shift%20when%20a%20local%20real%20estate%20agent%20sent%20me%20a%20DM%20on%20Instagram.%20She%20had%20clients%20who%20were%20looking%20for%20places%20to%20live%20temporarily%20until%20the%20house%20they%20were%20buying%20or%20renovating%20was%20available%20and%20the%20properties%20I%20managed%20were%20perfect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EBy%20January%202021%2C%20I%20was%20managing%204%20properties%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20January%202021%2C%20I%20was%20managing%20four%20properties%20and%20had%20to%20hire%20some%20help%20for%20the%20cleaning.%20Through%20word%20of%20mouth%2C%20I%20found%20an%20ex-nurse%20who'd%20started%20to%20offer%20cleaning%20services.%20She%20is%20now%20our%20full-time%20operations%20manager.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20April%202021%20we%20had%20to%20stop%20renting%20the%20barn%20because%20of%20new%20zoning%20regulations.%20That%20was%20the%20first%20bump%20in%20the%20road%2C%20but%20it%20didn't%20slow%20me%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20estate%20agent%20and%20I%20eventually%20went%20into%20partnership%20and%20launched%20Carriage%20House%20in%20August%202021.%20It's%20an%20umbrella%20company%20for%20her%20real-estate%20company%20and%20Be%20Still%20Getaways%20that%20offers%20move-in%20ready%20homes%20for%20short-term%20investment%20properties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWorking%20with%20a%20local%20real%20estate%20agent%20streamlined%20my%20business%20model%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20sells%20short-term%20rental%20properties%20as%20investment%20opportunities%2C%20and%20I%20manage%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20suggest%20that%20anyone%20who%20runs%20an%20Airbnb%20connects%20with%20the%20Realtor%20in%20their%20community%20with%20the%20best%20reviews.%20That%20person%20will%20know%20all%20the%20contractors%2C%20plumbers%2C%20and%20electricians.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20the%20projects%20I%20took%20on%20were%20facelifts%3B%20now%20Carriage%20House%20works%20on%20full-scale%20rehab%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Be%20Still%20Getaways%20luxury%20apartment%20in%20Virginia%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6530f0d096f7540cd0602619%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWorking%20with%20a%20local%20real%20estate%20agent%20meant%20Inlow%20could%20be%20more%20picky%20about%20the%20projects%20she%20took%20on.%3Cp%3EBe%20Still%20Getaways%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Interior%20of%20a%20Be%20Still%20Getaway%20logde%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6530f153be9edfa8eda4759e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBe%20Still%20Getaways%20prioritizes%20the%20aesthetics%20of%20the%20short-term%20rentals%20they%20manage.%3Cp%3EBe%20Still%20Getaways%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spent%20the%20first%20couple%20of%20years%20learning%20about%20the%20business%20and%20understanding%20the%20market.%20The%20units%20that%20I%20rented%20were%20based%20on%20what%20the%20owners%20came%20to%20me%20with.%20This%20still%20happens%2C%20but%20now%20my%20partner%20will%20match%20potential%20investment%20properties%20with%20investors%20and%20then%20the%20Be%20Still%20Getaways%20team%20will%20give%20the%20property%20a%20makeover.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20control%20of%20the%20design%20process%20gives%20us%20an%20edge%2C%20and%20I%20strongly%20believe%20shaping%20each%20property%20in%20our%20unique%20style%20has%20contributed%20to%20our%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20can%20turn%20around%20smaller%20units%20in%20two%20weeks%2C%20but%20large%20units%20that%20need%20renovations%20and%20architect%20meetings%20and%20involve%20engineers%20can%20take%20three%20months%20to%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMy%20partner%20and%20I%20run%20this%20Airbnb%20business%20full%20time%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20leave%20my%20consultancy%20job%20until%20July%202022%20as%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20were%20also%20building%20our%20family%20home.%20We%20had%20made%20%24300%2C000%20in%20revenue%20in%20the%20first%20half%20of%20that%20year%2C%20and%20our%20future%20pipeline%20looked%20strong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20worked%20as%20a%20teacher%20before%20he%20joined%20the%20team%20in%20June%202023%20to%20oversee%20our%20lawn%20care.%20Some%20of%20our%20properties%20have%20acres%20of%20land.%20With%20the%20homes%2C%20inns%2C%20and%20motels%2C%20we%20now%20manage%20133%20individual%20listings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EContracts%20with%20owners%20ebb%20and%20flow%20and%20not%20all%20travelers%20are%20looking%20for%20the%20same%20type%20of%20getaway%2C%20so%20having%20an%20array%20of%20properties%20has%20helped%20our%20business.%20We%20now%20have%20seven%20employees%20and%2050%20contractors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20stylish%20interior%20of%20a%20Be%20Still%20Getaways%20property.%