ef%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fshark-tank-kevin-oleary-small-business-fed-cash-crunch-crisis-2023-7%5C%22%3Efacing%20a%20credit%20crunch%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20flagged%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frecession-outlook-were-not-in-the-clear-yet-soft-landing-2023-10%5C%22%3Eslowdown%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20America's%20services%20sector%20during%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D0ef440e0b2c5da3b8f76df8c6eec3ff995b1a89f53e936ad8021fdce7465f0a1%26postID%3D652ff8d7e223f7c3e11ccdd8%26postSlug%3Dcardboard-box-recession-services-inflation-economy-outlook-charles-schwab-kleintop-2023-10%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.morningstar.com%252Fpodcasts%252Fthe-long-view%252Fa85638f2-5e28-4d57-b416-9c996631a5a3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecent%20episode%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Long%20View%26quot%3B%20podcast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECharles%20Schwab's%20chief%20global%20investment%20strategist%20also%20cautioned%20the%20economic%20picture%20has%20changed%20drastically%20in%20the%20past%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20suggested%20inflation%20may%20prove%20stubborn%2C%20and%20highlighted%20several%20other%20risks%20to%20investors'%20portfolios.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKleintop%20touched%20on%20everything%20from%20Taylor%20Swift%20and%20Beyonc%C3%A9%20to%20Walt%20Disney%20World%20and%20roach%20motels%20during%20the%20wide-ranging%20conversation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHere%20are%20Kleintop's%2010%20best%20quotes%2C%20lightly%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E1.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20a%20data%20junkie.%20I%20get%20up%20in%20the%20morning%20and%20I%20plug%20my%20Bloomberg%20in%20like%20an%20IV.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E2.%20%26quot%3BIf%20I'm%20on%20a%20desert%20island%20and%20I%20can%20only%20get%20one%20piece%20of%20economic%20data%20%E2%80%94%20because%20what%20else%20would%20you%20want%20on%20a%20desert%20island%3F%20Maybe%20you're%20a%20Beyonc%C3%A9%20and%20a%20bottle-of-rum%20person.%20I%20am%20a%20PMI%20guy.%20I%20love%20the%20Purchasing%20Managers'%20Index.%20I%20think%20it's%20a%20wonderful%20tool.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E3.%20%26quot%3BI%20find%20comfort%20in%20looking%20at%20the%20plunging%20demand%20for%20cardboard%20boxes.%20I've%20been%20referring%20to%20this%20as%20a%20'cardboard%20box%20recession'%20because%20things%20that%20are%20manufactured%20and%20shipped%20tend%20to%20go%20in%20a%20box%2C%20and%20because%20demand%20for%20corrugated%20fiberboard%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20what%20most%20cardboard%20boxes%20are%20made%20from%20%E2%80%94%20has%20fallen%20just%20like%20it%20did%20in%20past%20recessions.%20So%2C%20literally%2C%20cardboard%20boxes%20are%20in%20a%20recession.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E4.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20a%20florist%20and%20you%20were%20thinking%20about%20buying%20that%20extra%20truck%20and%20staffing%20it%2C%20it's%20hard%20to%20do%20that%20now.%20Banks%20are%20demanding%20more%20collateral%2C%20higher%20rates%2C%20qualifying%20fewer%20borrowers.%20So%2C%20things%20are%20getting%20tighter.%26quot%3B%20(Kleintop%20was%20highlighting%20that%20many%20small%20businesses%20are%20finding%20it%20harder%20to%20borrow.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E5.%20%26quot%3BWe%20know%20travel%20and%20entertainment%20have%20been%20strong%20%E2%80%94%20just%20ask%20Taylor%20Swift.%20It's%20been%20big%2C%20but%20it's%20coming%20down.%20We've%20heard%20that%20from%20airlines.%20You're%20seeing%20higher%20vacancies%20at%20hotels%2C%20more%20open%20reservations%20on%20OpenTable.com.%20I%20live%20three%20miles%20from%20Walt%20Disney%20World%20here%20in%20Florida.%20You%20know%20what%3F%20You%20can%20actually%20get%20on%20Space%20Mountain%20lately.%20You%20don't%20have%20to%20wait%20two%20hours.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E6.%20%26quot%3BAll%20these%20signs%20are%20indicating%20that%20we're%20seeing%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20slowdown%20in%20the%20services%20sector.%20That's%20important%20because%20there%20are%2010%20times%20as%20many%20services%20jobs%20as%20manufacturing%20jobs%20in%20the%20US.%20If%20we%20start%20to%20see%20the%20service%20sector%20reflect%20more%20signs%20of%20this%20slowdown%20in%20demand%2C%20well%2C%20we%20might%20see%20a%20weakening%20labor%20market%2C%20and%20then%20that%20could%20feed%20into%20the%20retail%20space%2C%20and%20construction%2C%20and%20so%20many%20other%20areas.%20Not%20a%20deep%20downturn%2C%20but%20even%20a%20small%20pullback%20there%20could%20really%20mean%20a%20lot%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20labor%20market.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E7.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20very%20different%20environment%20in%20terms%20of%20inflation%2C%20valuations%2C%20interest%20rates%2C%20and%20credit%20conditions%20%E2%80%94%20very%20different%20from%20the%20last%20cycle%2C%20leading%20to%20very%20different%20leadership%20in%20the%20market.%20We've%20turned%20the%20corner%20on%20a%20new%20cycle%2C%20whether%20we%20ultimately%20define%20what%20we're%20experiencing%20right%20now%20as%20an%20official%20recession%20or%20not.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E8.%20%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20experience%20with%20QT.%20It's%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20a%20roach%20motel.%20Like%20you%20can%20check%20into%20QE%2C%20but%20it's%20real%20hard%20to%20check%20back%20out%20again.%20(Kleintop%20was%20referring%20to%20quantitative%20tightening%2C%20where%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20shrinks%20its%20balance%20sheet%20to%20cool%20the%20economy%2C%20and%20quantitative%20easing%2C%20where%20it%20buys%20bonds%20to%20stimulate%20growth.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E9.%20%26quot%3BThe%20market%20is%20enamored%20of%20this%20idea%20that%20everything%20is%20going%20to%20be%20turning%20around%20quickly%20next%20year.%20We%20just%20don't%20see%20that.%26quot%3B%20(Kleintop%20warned%20that%20inflation%20has%20rarely%20plunged%20and%20stayed%20flat%20and%20low%20in%20past%20cycles%2C%20and%20suggested%20a%20period%20of%20higher%2C%20more%20volatile%20price%20growth%20was%20likely.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E10.%20%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20know%20how%20deep%20and%20how%20broad%20this%20is.%20We%20have%20a%20sense%20of%20it%2C%20but%20it's%20been%20going%20on%20for%20so%20long.%20It's%20one%20of%20those%20things%20where%20you%20just%20don't%20know%20how%20many%20things%20could%20get%20broken%20when%20it%20starts%20to%20move.%26quot%3B%20(Kleintop%20was%20flagging%20the%20risk%20that%20Japan%20may%20raise%20interest%20rates%20and%20strengthen%20the%20yen%2C%20disrupting%20the%20popular%20%26quot%3Byen%20carry%20trade%26quot%3B%20where%20investors%20borrow%20cheaply%20in%20Japan%20then%20invest%20the%20funds%20for%20a%20higher%20return%20elsewhere.%20He%20warned%20there%20could%20be%20mass%20selling%20of%20dollar-based%20investments%20and%20other%20high-yielding%20currencies%20and%20assets.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcardboard-box-recession-services-inflation-economy-outlook-charles-schwab-kleintop-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697706624000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652ffee896f7540cd05f639a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcardboard-box-recession-services-inflation-economy-outlook-charles-schwab-kleintop-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Charles%20Schwab's%20Jeffrey%20Kleintop%20touched%20on%20everything%20from%20Taylor%20Swift%20and%20Beyonc%C3%A9%20to%20the%20credit%20crunch%20squeezing%20small%20businesses.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tmohamed%40insider.com%20(Theron%20Mohamed)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcardboard-box-recession-services-inflation-economy-outlook-charles-schwab-kleintop-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Who%20Is%20Gaurav%20Taneja%3F%20YouTuber%20Who%20Claims%20To%20Earn%20More%20Than%20AirAsia%20CEO%22%2C%2