rt%20Process%20On%20Nov%2023%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrivate%20schools%20in%20Delhi%20will%20begin%20the%20registration%20process%20for%20students%20in%20nursery%2C%20pre-primary%20(KG)%2C%20and%20Class%201%20from%20November%2023%2C%20as%20per%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edudel.nic.in%2Fupload%2Fupload_2023_24%2F8873_8882_dt_18102023.PDF%5C%22%3Enotification%3C%2Fa%3E%20issued%20by%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Education%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20October%2018.%20The%20deadline%20for%20registration%20is%20December%2015%2C%20and%20the%20first%20admission%20list%20will%20be%20released%20on%20January%2012%2C%202024.%20Private%20schools%20are%20required%20to%20allocate%2025%20percent%20of%20their%20seats%20for%20economically%20disadvantaged%20(EWS)%20and%20underprivileged%20students%2C%20as%20well%20as%20children%20with%20disabilities.%20Separate%20lists%20will%20be%20provided%20for%20these%20categories.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20notification%2C%20the%20minimum%20age%20requirements%20for%20admission%20to%20pre-school%20(nursery)%2C%20pre-primary%20(KG)%2C%20and%20Class%201%20are%20three%20years%2C%20four%20years%2C%20and%20five%20years%2C%20respectively%2C%20as%20of%20March%2031.%20The%20notification%20categorises%20pre-school%2C%20pre-primary%2C%20and%20Class%201%20as%20entry-level%20classes%20and%20specifies%20that%20the%20maximum%20age%20limits%20for%20admission%20should%20be%20under%20four%20years%20for%20pre-school%2C%20under%20five%20years%20for%20pre-primary%2C%20and%20under%20six%20years%20for%20Class%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20publication%20of%20the%20first%20admission%20list%2C%20schools%20can%20address%20parental%20inquiries%20from%20January%2013%20to%20January%2022%2C%20as%20outlined%20in%20the%20notification.%20The%20notification%20states%20that%20parents%20may%20contact%20the%20school's%20head%20or%20principal%20if%20they%20wish%20to%20request%20age%20relaxation%20through%20a%20manual%20application%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%2