20heads%20and%20stealing%20the%20hearts%20of%20Gen%20X%20diners.%20Cava%2C%20billed%20as%20a%20Mediterranean%20version%20of%20Chipotle%2C%20went%20public%20in%20June%20and%20is%20red%20hot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20visited%20Cava%20several%20times%20over%20the%20past%20year.%20On%20each%20visit%2C%20lines%20at%20lunch%20and%20dinner%20snake%20to%20the%20back%20of%20the%20restaurant%20and%20wrap%20around%20the%20dining%20room.%20According%20to%20a%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Ftiktokers-claim-downfall-of-chipotle-rise-of-cava-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20viral%20video%20by%20a%20TikTok%20influencer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Chipotle%20%26quot%3Bdoesn't%20hit%20the%20way%20it%20used%20to%26quot%3B%20with%20fans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20I%20set%20out%20to%20compare%20Cava%20and%20Chipotle%20in%20a%20head-to-head%20battle.%20To%20keep%20it%20simple%2C%20I%20compared%20Chipotle's%20burritos%20and%20bowls%20to%20Cava's%20pitas%20and%20bowls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20tight%20race.%20Ultimately%2C%20fate%20helped%20me%20crown%20a%20champion.%20Here's%20what%20I%20discovered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E(Note%3A%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EPrices%20reflect%20purchases%20made%20at%20Chipotle%20and%20Cava%20stores%20in%20Orange%20County%2C%20California.%20Prices%20may%20vary%20where%20you%20live.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20visited%20a%20Chipotle%20in%20a%20college%20town%20near%20my%20house.%20I%20stood%20around%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20minutes%20before%20someone%20decided%20to%20help%20me.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nancy%20Luna%20waits%20for%20someone%20to%20help%20her%20at%20Chipotle.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652eedb296f7540cd05ed294%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EInsider%20reporter%20Nancy%20Luna%20waits%20for%20someone%20to%20help%20her%20at%20Chipotle.%3Cp%3EInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spotte