Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ECava%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20always%20has%20long%20lines.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Long%20lines%20at%20Cava.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652f0931211def8ed837b8dd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECava%20always%20seems%20to%20have%20a%20long%20line%20when%20I%20visit.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20visited%20Cava%20about%20four%20times%20over%20the%20past%20year.%20At%20lunch%20and%20dinner%2C%20each%20location%20commands%20crowds.%20And%20like%20the%20early%20days%20of%20Chipotle%2C%20customers%20don't%20seem%20to%20mind%20waiting%20in%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EChipotle%20prices%20its%20bowls%20by%20the%20type%20of%20protein%20you%20select.%20I%20ordered%20mine%20with%20carne%20asada%2C%20a%20premium%20protein%20available%20for%20a%20limited%20time%20only.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Approximately%2065%25%20of%20all%20Chipotle%20digital%20orders%20are%20bowls%20or%20salads.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652efe46211def8ed837b036%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EApproximately%2065%25%20of%20all%20Chipotle%20digital%20orders%20are%20bowls%20or%20salads.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20carne%20asada's%20third%20time%20on%20the%20Chipotle%20menu%20after%20first%20debuting%20as%20a%20limited-time%20offer%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fan%20favorite%20is%20top%20sirloin%20and%20tri-tip%20steak%20strips%20seasoned%20with%20cumin%2C%20coriander%2C%20and%20oregano.%20It%20comes%20at%20a%20premium%20price%20%E2%80%93%20%2411.85.%20Other%20proteins%20on%20the%20menu%20ranged%20in%20price%20from%20%248.85%20to%20%2410.60.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20used%20to%20think%20the%20topping%20options%20at%20Chipotle%20were%20plentiful.%20But%20after%20eating%20at%20Cava%2C%20the%20Chipotle%20choices%20seem%20boring%20and%20scarce.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Someone%20dolloping%20guacamole%20on%20a%20Chipotle%20bowl.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F641201588215b5001814838d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIf%20you%20eliminate%20the%20four%20salsa%20options%2C%20the%20remaining%20free%20toppings%20at%20Chipotle%20are%20sour%20cream%2C%20shredded%20cheese%2C%20fajita%20veggies%2C%20and%20romaine%20lettuce.%20That's%20not%20that%20much%20compared%20to%20Cava.%3Cp%3EJoe%20Raedle%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20selecting%20your%20beans%2C%20rice%2C%20and%20protein%2C%20Chipotle%20offers%20eight%20toppings%20for%20free%20to%20customize%20your%20bowl%3A%20fresh%20tomato%20salsa%2C%20roasted%20chili%20corn%20salsa%2C%20tomatillo-green%20chili%20salsa%2C%20tomatillo-red%20salsa%2C%20sour%20cream%2C%20shredded%20cheese%2C%20fajita%20veggies%2C%20and%20romaine%20lettuce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20chose%20all%20the%20free%20options%20except%20the%20tomatillo-red%20salsa%2C%20which%20is%20too%20spicy%20for%20my%20palate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECustomers%20can%20add%20guacamole%20(%242.65)%20and%20queso%20blanco%20(%241.70)%20for%20an%20upcharge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20eliminate%20the%20salsa%20options%2C%20there%20are%20only%20four%20free%20topping%20choices%20at%20Chipotle.%20That's%20underwhelming%20when%20compared%20to%20Cava.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAs%20I%20ordered%20along%20the%20assembly%20line%2C%20I%20noticed%20all%20the%20food%20bins%20were%20practically%20empty.%20I%20got%20the%20last%20scoopful%20of%20many%20items%2C%20including%20the%20carne.%20asada%2C%20which%20wasn't%20a%20good%20sign%20that%20I%20was%20getting%20fresh%20products.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221473%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chipotle%20burrito%20and%20bowl.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652f003396f7540cd05eed01%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221105%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EInsider%20food%20correspondent%20Nancy%20Luna%20ordered%20a%20custom%20bowl%20and%20burrito%20at%20Chipotle%2C%20and%C2%A0%20compared%20it%20to%20Cava's%20bowl%20and%20pita.%3Cp%3EInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Chipotle%20bowl%20did%20not%20meet%20my%20expectations%20because%20the%20ingredients%20didn't%20taste%20fresh.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chain%20describes%20the%20carne%20asada%20as%20juicy%20strips%20of%20steak%20seasoned%20with%20spices%20and%20topped%20with%20a%20squeeze%20of%20lime.%20But%20I%20couldn't%20taste%20any%20of%20those%20craveable%20flavors.%20The%20steak%20was%20dry%20and%20lukewarm%20to%20the%20touch%2C%20underscoring%20my%20suspicions%20that%20I%20was%20getting%20the%20dregs%20of%20the%20carne%20asada%20sitting%20in%20the%20bin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMy%20bowl%20experience%20at%20Cava%20was%20quite%20different.%20I%20was%20overwhelmed%20with%20the%20variety%20of%20options.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20customized%20bowl%20from%20Cava.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652f00d9211def8ed837b223%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENancy%20Luna%20tried%20Cava's%20fresh%20lemonade%20beverages%20along%20with%20her%20bowl.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Chipotle%20has%20two%20base%20grain%20options%20(white%20or%20brown%20rice)%2C%20Cava%20offers%20nine%20different%20choices%20of%20grains%20and%20greens.%20Almost%20all%20of%20them%20are%20irresistible%2C%20making%20it%20hard%20to%20choose.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECava's%20base%20choices%20are%20black%20lentils%2C%20saffron%20basmati%20rice%2C%20brown%20rice%2C%20arugula%2C%20Supergreens%20(a%20blend%20of%20raw%20cabbage%2C%20Brussels%20sprouts%2C%20broccoli%2C%20and%20kale)%2C%20baby%20spinach%2C%20romaine%2C%20Splendidgreens%20(a%20mix%20of%20chopped%20romaine%2C%20radicchio%2C%20escarole%2C%20chicory%20endive%2C%20and%20cabbage)%20and%20RightRice.%20The%20latter%20is%20a%20high-protein%20veggie%20rice%20available%20for%20a%20%241.35%20upcharge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20ingredients%20are%20super%20appealing%20to%20anyone%20looking%20for%20healthy%20high-fiber%20choices%20in%20their%20diet.%20I've%20tasted%20nearly%20all%20of%20these%20options%20except%20the%20spinach.%20I'm%20not%20a%20fan%20of%20Popeye's%20fave%20greens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20RightRice%20is%20a%20solid%2C%20lower-carb%20grain%20that's%20better%20in%20taste%20and%20texture%20than%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fchipotle-new-cauliflower-rice-taste-test-review-2021-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChipotle's%20cilantro-lime%20cauliflower%20rice%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20alt-rice%20is%20no%20longer%20on%20the%20menu%20after%20launching%20nationwide%20for%20a%20limited%20time%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECava%20knows%20its%20choices%20are%20tempting%2C%20as%20the%20chain%20allows%20you%20to%20choose%20two%20options%20as%20one%20base.%20I%20chose%20black%20lentils%20and%20brown%20rice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EUnlike%20Chipotle%2C%20the%20topping%20options%20at%20Cava%20are%20dreamy%20and%20craveworthy.%20That%E2%80%99s%20probably%20why%20the%20lines%20get%20clogged%20because%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20lot%20of%20tempting%20choices%20to%20select.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cava%20offers%20plentiful%20topping%20options.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652f023696f7540cd05eee63%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECava%20offers%20plentiful%20topping%20options.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECava's%20main%20entree%20options%20include%20harissa%20honey%20chicken%2C%20spicy%20lamb%20meatballs%2C%20grilled%20chicken%2C%20braised%20lamb%2C%20spicy%20falafel%2C%20falafel%2C%20and%20roasted%20vegetables.%20Customers%20can%20choose%20one%20main%2C%20or%20two%20with%20the%20portion%20sizes%20split%20in%20half.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20chose%20the%20braised%20lamb%20and%20falafel.%20A%20custom%20build-your-own%20bowl%20or%20pita%20cost%20%2411.75.%20Unlike%20Chipotle%2C%20the%20base%20price%20doesn't%20change%20for%20most%20main%20entrees%20chosen.%20There%20is%20an%20upcharge%20for%20the%20harissa%20honey%20chicken%20and%20the%20spicy%20lamb%20meatballs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ECava%20is%20a%20bit%20more%20expensive%20than%20Chipotle.%20But%20the%20trade-off%20is%20you%20get%20more%20exciting%20dips%2C%20dressings%2C%20and%20topping%20to%20choose%20from.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cava%20topping%20choices.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652f038496f7540cd05eef97%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECava%20offers%20many%20more%20craveworthy%20topping%20choices%20than%20Chipotle.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECustomers%20can%20choose%20up%20to%20three%20of%20the%20six%20different%20dip%20options.%20They%20come%20in%20melon%20baller-size%20scoops.%20I%20got%20hummus%2C%20tzatziki%2C%20and%20roasted%20eggplant.%20I%20passed%20on%20the%20other%20three%20options%20%E2%80%93%20crazy%20feta%20(whipped%20with%20jalapenos)%2C%20red%20pepper%20hummus%2C%20and%20harissa%20%E2%80%93%20because%20they%20are%20too%20spicy%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20no%20extra%20cost%2C%20Cava%20offers%2012%20unlimited%20topping%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChoose%20as%20many%20as%20you%20want%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20sign%20on%20the%20window%20display.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAvocado%20is%20also%20available%20for%20a%20%242.45%20upcharge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20topping%20choices%20are%20much%20more%20compelling%20than%20anything%20offered%20at%20Chipotle.%20I%20chose%20salt-brined%20pickles%2C%20kalamata%20olives%2C%20pita%20crisps%2C%20tomato%20and%20onion%2C%20crumbled%20feta%2C%20and%20Persian%20cucumbers.%20The%20result%20is%20a%20hefty%20bowl%20filled%20with%20crazy-good%20ingredients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWinner%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20The%20Cava%20bowl%20wins%20on%20value%2C%20taste%2C%20and%20freshness.%20Even%20though%20Cava%20is%20more%20expensive%20than%20Chipotle%2C%20I%20am%20willing%20to%20pay%20a%20couple%20of%20extra%20bucks%20for%20the%20sheer%20volume%20of%20flavors%20packed%20in%20the%20chain's%20bowls.%20It's%20a%20better%20bang%20for%20my%20buck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhile%20Cava%E2%80%99s%20bowls%20are%20a%20thing%20of%20beauty%2C%20their%20pitas%20are%20ugly%20and%20messy.%20You%20need%20a%20smock%20to%20eat%20these%20bulging%20wraps.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cava's%20pita%20wraps%20are%20bigger%20than%20Chipotle's%20burritos%2C%20but%20messy.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652f05b7211def8ed837b692%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECava's%20pita%20wraps%20are%20bigger%20than%20Chipotle's%20burritos%2C%20but%20messy.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20choose%20a%20lot%20of%20toppings%20for%20a%20bowl%20at%20Cava%2C%20it%20doesn't%20impact%20the%20presentation%20of%20the%20meal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20when%20you%20select%20numerous%20toppings%20for%20the%20pita%2C%20you%20end%20up%20building%20a%20messy%20monster%20of%20a%20wrap.%20When%20biting%20into%20the%20unwieldy%20pita%2C%20ingredients%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20wrap%20ooze%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20pita%20is%20in%20a%20constant%20state%20of%20falling%20apart.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20handheld%20meal%20that%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20hold.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cava's%20pita%20wraps%20are%20messy.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652f0550be9edfa8eda34c08%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECava's%20bulging%20pita%20wraps%20are%20messy.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20pita%20is%20delicious%2C%20I%20end%20up%20eating%20it%20with%20a%20fork%20like%20it's%20a%20bowl%20or%20salad%20because%20it's%20too%20hard%20to%20pick%20up%20and%20eat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20base%20price%20of%20the%20pita%20was%20%2411.75.%20But%20because%20I%20chose%20a%20premium%20protein%20%E2%80%93%20lamb%20meatballs%20%E2%80%93%20Cava%20charged%20me%20an%20extra%20%242.30.%20I%20also%20added%20guacamole%2C%20bringing%20the%20total%20price%20of%20the%20pita%20to%20%2416.50.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAt%20Chipotle%2C%20I%20created%20a%20custom-built%20burrito%20with%20barbacoa%2C%20cheese%2C%20guacamole%2C%20salsas%2C%20queso%20blanco%2C%20and%20no%20rice.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chipotle's%20burrito.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652f061996f7540cd05ef16b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChipotle%20offers%20big%20foil-wrapped%20burritos%2C%20created%20your%20way%20in%20a%20walk-along%20setup%20like%20Subway.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20burrito%20was%20amazing.%20Barbacoa%20is%20one%20of%20Chipotle's%20best%20proteins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20upcharges%20for%20the%20premium%20sides%2C%20the%20%2410.60%20burrito%20turned%20into%20a%20%2414.95%20meal.%20My%20burrito%20was%20big%20and%20much%20easier%20to%20handle%20compared%20to%20Cava's%20pita.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETip%3A%20If%20you're%20trying%20to%20save%20a%20buck%2C%20steer%20clear%20of%20the%20premium%20proteins%20and%20sides%20at%20both%20chains.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWinner%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20My%20Chipotle%20burrito%20was%20delicious%20and%20easy%20to%20eat.%20Cava's%20pita%20was%20also%20delicious%2C%20but%20it%20fails%20on%20presentation.%20It's%20just%20too%20messy%20to%20order.%20So%20Chipotle%20wins%20this%20round.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESpeaking%20of%20big%20burritos%2C%20I'll%20digress%20a%20bit.%20Are%20Chipotle's%20burritos%20getting%20smaller%3F%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chipotle's%20burrito%20compared%20to%20Cava's%20pita.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652f0651211def8ed837b6fc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChipotle's%20burrito%20compared%20to%20Cava's%20pita.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EChipotle%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchipotle-mobile-order-burritos-werent-smaller-in-testphotos-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshrinkflation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20making%20their%20burritos%20smaller%20even%20though%20they've%20been%20raising%20prices.%20I%20did%20not%20find%20that%20to%20be%20true.%20My%20burrito%2C%20while%20smaller%20than%20Cava's%20massive%20wraps%2C%20was%20still%20big.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20I%20asked%20for%20no%20rice%2C%20a%20filler%20that%20makes%20the%20burritos%20bulge%20even%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Chipotle%2C%20which%20recently%20said%20it%20would%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchipotle-mexican-grill-prices-are-rising-menu-increase-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eraise%20prices%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20fourth%20time%20in%20two%20years%2C%20told%20me%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20haven't%20made%20any%20changes%20to%20our%20portion%20sizes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EClearly%2C%20I%20needed%20a%20tie-breaker%2C%20so%20I%20looked%20at%20the%20chains'%20sides%20and%20dips.%20%3Cfigure%