rl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fus-president-biden-to-address-nation-on-israel-ukraine-as-crises-mount%2Farticleshow%2F104550867.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fus-president-biden-to-address-nation-on-israel-ukraine-as-crises-mount%2Famp_articleshow%2F104550867.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fus-president-biden-to-address-nation-on-israel-ukraine-as-crises-mount%2Famp_articleshow%2F104550867.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20No%20Cases%20Against%20KCR%3A%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20Alleges%203-Party%20Nexus%20In%20Telangana%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThrowing%20a%20new%20poll%20challenge%20to%20Telangana%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20chief%20K%20Chandrashekar%20Rao%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20questioned%20his%20silence%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20caste%20census%20and%20said%20his%20party%20will%20get%20the%20survey%20done%20if%20it%20comes%20to%20power%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20already%20initiated%20caste%20census%20surveys%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20and%20Karnataka%20and%20will%20do%20the%20same%20in%20Telangana%20as%20soon%20as%20we%20come%20to%20power.%20The%20caste%20census%20will%20reveal%20how%20much%20KCR's%20family%20has%20looted%20Telangana%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gandhi%20said%20while%20addressing%20a%20roadshow%20in%20Telangana's%20Bhupalpally.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20leader%20alleged%20that%20the%20BRS%20and%20the%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi-led%20AIMIM%20are%20collaborating%20with%20the%20BJP%20and%20launching%20a%20joint%20attack%20on%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20Prime%20Minister%20(Narendra)%20Modi%20and%20Chief%20Minister%20KCR%20deliver%20speeches%2C%20the%20people%20of%20Telangana%20should%20question%20them%20about%20when%20they%20intend%20to%20conduct%20the%20caste%20census%20survey%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20he%20alleged%2C%20is%20filing%20cases%20against%20Opposition%20parties%20to%20silence%20them%2C%20but%20there%20are%20no%20cases%20against%20KCR.%20%26quot%3BThe%20absence%20of%20CBI%20and%20ED%20cases%20against%20Chief%20Minister%20KCR%20raises%20questions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELaunching%20a%20dynasty%20attack%20on%20the%20BRS%2C%20he%20said%20people%20of%20Telangana%2C%20which%20got%20statehood%20in%202014%2C%20had%20dreamed%20of%20a%20state%20where%20the%20common%20man%20would%20govern.%20%26quot%3BBut%20in%20the%20last%20ten%20years%2C%20your%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20KCR%2C%20has%20distanced%20himself%20from%20the%20people%2C%20and%20only%20his%20family%20is%20ruling%20the%20state.%20He%20has%20shattered%20your%20dream%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECaste%20census%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20said%2C%20is%20the%20most%20pressing%20issue%20in%20the%20country.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20like%20an%20x-ray%20that%20reveals%20the%20percentage%20of%20backward%20classes%2C%20SC%2C%20ST%2C%20and%20minorities%2C%20enabling%20equitable%20budget%20allocation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESaying%20that%20it%20was%20a%20Congress-led%20government%20that%20fulfilled%20the%20statehood%20promise%20to%20Telangana%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BMy%20relationship%20with%20the%20people%20of%20Telangana%20is%20one%20of%20love%20and%20affection.%20While%20KCR%20and%20Modi%20come%20to%20Telangana%20for%20a%20political%20relationship%20with%20you%2C%20my%20connection%20with%20you%20is%20based%20on%20love%20and%20affection.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETelangana%2C%20he%20claimed%2C%20has%20the%20highest%20corruption%20in%20India%20and%20this%20adversely%20affects%20the%20youth%20and%20women%20of%20Telangana.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWaving%20to%20the%20people%20gathered%20on%20terraces%20and%20the%20roadside%20during%20the%20Congress%20march%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BLooking%20at%20your%20enthusiasm%2C%20it%20seems%20likely%20that%20KCR%20is%20going%20to%20lose%20this%20election.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20caste%20census%20issue%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20subject%20of%20heated%20exchanges%20between%20the%20BRS%20and%20the%20Congress%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20KCR's%20daughter%20and%20Legislative%20Council%20member%20K%20Kavitha%20had%20questioned%20why%20the%20Congress%20did%20not%20get%20a%20caste%20survey%20done%20in%20the%20six%20decades%20it%20governed%20the%20country.%20%26quot%3BThis%20Congress%20leader%20started%20talking%20about%20the%20census%20of%20the%20Backward%20Classes%20population.%20When%20they%20were%20in%20power%20for%2060%20years%2C%20they%20did%20not%20do%20it.%20Now%20he%20says%20he%20will%20do%20something%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20at%20Nizamabad%20last%20week%2C%20news%20agency%20PTI%20has%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIncidentally%2C%20the%20KCR%20government%20had%20got%20a%20caste%20survey%20done%20in%20the%20state%20in%202014%2C%20soon%20after%20it%20came%20to%20power.%20While%20results%20of%20the%20Samagra%20Kutumba%20Survey%20were%20not%20made%20public%20owing%20to%20litigations%20challenging%20it%2C%20the%20state%20government%20says%20it%20used%20the%20data%20for%20policy%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BRS%2C%20Ms%20Kavitha%20said%2C%20had%20conducted%20the%20survey%20and%20the%20results%20enabled%20it%20to%20effectively%20provide%20welfare%20schemes%20to%20all%20communities.%20She%20said%20Mr%20Gandhi%20just%20makes%20statements%20before%20elections%20unlike%20KCR%20who%20has%20prioritised%20the%20welfare%20of%20backward%20classes.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697705820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F58lbd0ag_rahul-gandhi-telangana_625x300_19_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-k-chandrashekar-rao-telangana-election-rahul-gandhi-throws-caste-census-challenge-at-kcr-ahead-of-telangana-poll