lding%20in%20Israel%20and%20Gaza%20may%20make%20us%20believe%20that%20we%20are%20heading%20for%20a%20polycrisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHow%20plausible%20is%20the%20likelihood%20of%20a%20polycrisis%20emerging%2C%20and%20importantly%2C%20what%20would%20be%20the%20impact%20on%20the%20Indian%20stock%20market%20and%20the%20Indian%20economy%20in%20general%3F%20The%20Ukraine%20war%20arguably%20had%20a%20limited%20impact%20on%20the%20US%20stock%20market%2C%20which%20was%20riding%20on%20AI%20stocks.%20India%20is%20a%20swing%20country%2C%20like%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20and%20it%20gained%20from%20the%20surge%20in%20its%20mid%20and%20small-cap%20stocks.%20But%20if%20it%20is%20not%20contained%20swiftly%2C%20the%20fallout%20of%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20conflict%20may%20inflict%20more%20catastrophic%20collateral%20damage%20on%20the%20global%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20fear%20that%20other%20countries%20could%20be%20drawn%20into%20this%20conflict.%20In%20particular%2C%20if%20Iran%2C%20Egypt%2C%20and%20Syria%20were%20to%20join%20this%20religious%20war%20%E2%80%93%20with%20the%20presumption%20that%20this%20war%20is%20affecting%20the%20sentiment%20of%20the%20Arab%20and%20Muslim%20world%20%E2%80%93%20the%C2%A0price%20of%20crude%20may%20spin%20out%20of%20control.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2023%2F10%2F13%2Foil-prices-crude-futures-rise-after-us-tightens-sanctions-on-russia.html%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2023%2F10%2F13%2Foil-prices-crude-futures-rise-after-us-tightens-sanctions-on-russia.html%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1697781640629000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw3I5iQvtlwVpNhfatk3tnj6%5C%22%3Eprice%20of%20crude%20oil%C2%A0has%20jumped%206%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%20the%20start%20of%20this%20crisis.%20The%20oil%20price%20has%20inched%20towards%20%2490%20a%20barrel%2C%20and%20it%20could%20cross%20the%20symbolic%20danger%20mark%20of%20%24100%20per%20barrel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp