ening%20ailments%2C%20often%20can%20only%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F2215363%2F%5C%22%3Eaccess%20needed%20services%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Israeli%20hospitals%20and%20require%20a%20permit%20to%20cross%20the%20border%20from%20Gaza.%20Some%20die%20before%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unicef.org%2Fmena%2Fdocuments%2Fgaza-strip-humanitarian-impact-15-years-blockade-june-2022%5C%22%3Epermit%20process%20is%20complete%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGaza%20health%20services%20after%20the%20siege%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20vulnerable%20health%20system%20is%20now%20facing%20unprecedented%20challenges%2C%20staffed%20by%20health%20professionals%20who%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Freliefweb.int%2Freport%2Foccupied-palestinian-territory%2Fprcs-statement-al-quds-hospital-evacuation-order-enar%5C%22%3Ecommitted%20to%20stay%20with%20their%20patients%3C%2Fa%3E%20even%20under%20hospital%20evacuation%20orders%20and%20at%20risk%20of%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20uncertain%20what%20the%20health%20system%20of%20Gaza%20will%20look%20like%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20years%20past%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farabcenterdc.org%2Fresource%2Frebuilding-gaza-yet-again%2F%5C%22%3Einternational%20aid%20would%20help%20repair%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20rebuild%20some%2C%20but%20not%20all%2C%20of%20the%20infrastructure%20damaged%20in%20airstrikes%2C%20especially%20schools%20and%20hospitals.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20has%20promised%20a%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F10%2F08%2Fworld%2Fmiddleeast%2Fhamas-israel-netanyahu-gaza.html%5C%22%3Elong%20and%20difficult%20war%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%20And%20with%20the%20level%20of%20destruction%20seen%20in%20just%20a%20few%20days%2C%20it%20remains%20unclear%20just%20what%20will%20be%20left%20in%20the%20aftermath.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlready%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%