22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fkorean%2Fsee-you-in-my-19th-life-actress-shin-hye-sun-clarifies-on-rumours-about-drinking-20-bottles-of-soju%2Farticleshow%2F104548456.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Christ's%20Picture%20At%20Home%20Doesn't%20Mean%20Person%20Has%20Converted%3A%20High%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMerely%20having%20a%20picture%20of%20Jesus%20Christ%20in%20a%20house%20does%20not%20mean%20that%20a%20person%20has%20converted%20to%20Christianity%2C%20the%20Nagpur%20bench%20of%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20division%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Prithviraj%20Chavan%20and%20Urmila%20Joshi%20Phalke%20on%20October%2010%20allowed%20a%20petition%20filed%20by%20a%2017-year-old%20girl%20challenging%20a%20September%202022%20order%20passed%20by%20the%20Amravati%20District%20Caste%20Certificate%20Scrutiny%20Committee%20invalidating%20her%20caste%20as%20'Mahar'.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20of%20the%20vigilance%20officer%20(of%20the%20committee)%20needs%20to%20be%20discarded%20at%20the%20threshold%20as%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20the%20petitioner's%20family%20follows%20the%20tradition%20of%20Buddhism%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20invalidating%20her%20caste%20claim%20was%20taken%20after%20the%20committee's%20vigilance%20cell%20conducted%20an%20inquiry%20and%20found%20that%20the%20petitioner's%20father%20and%20grandfather%20had%20converted%20to%20Christianity%20and%20a%20picture%20of%20Jesus%20Christ%20was%20found%20displayed%20in%20their%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%2C%20they%20converted%20to%20Christianity%2C%20they%20are%20included%20in%20the%20category%20of%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%2C%20the%20committee%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioner%20girl%20claimed%20the%20picture%20of%20Jesus%20Christ%20was%20gifted%20to%20them%20by%20someone%20and%20they%20had%20just%20displayed%20it%20in%20their%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20bench%20in%20its%20order%20noted%20there%20was%20absolutely%20no%20shred%20of%20evidence%20found%20by%20the%20vigilance%20cell%20during%20inquiry%20that%20either%20the%20grandfather%2C%20father%20or%20the%20petitioner%20had%20undergone%20baptism%20in%20order%20to%20buttress%20the%20committee's%20contention%20that%20the%20petitioner's%20family%20had%20converted%20to%20Christianity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20sane%20man%20will%20accept%20or%20believe%20that%20merely%20because%20there%20is%20a%20picture%20of%20Jesus%20Christ%20in%20the%20house%20would%20ipso%20facto%20mean%20that%20a%20person%20had%20converted%20himself%20into%20Christianity%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBaptism%20is%20a%20Christian%20sacrament%20by%20which%20one%20is%20received%20in%20Church%20and%20sometimes%20given%20a%20name%2C%20generally%20involving%20the%20candidate%20is%20to%20be%20anointed%20with%20or%20submerged%20in%20water%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMerely%20because%20the%20vigilance%20cell%20officer%2C%20during%20his%20visit%20to%20the%20house%20of%20the%20petitioner%2C%20noticed%20a%20picture%20of%20Lord%20Jesus%20Christ%2C%20he%20assumed%20the%20petitioner's%20family%20professes%20Christian%20religion%2C%20the%20high%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20of%20the%20vigilance%20officer%20needs%20to%20be%20discarded%20at%20the%20threshold%20as%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20the%20petitioner's%20family%20follows%20the%20tradition%20of%20Buddhism%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioner%20relied%20on%20the%20'Mahar'%20caste%20certificates%20issued%20in%20the%20past%20to%20her%20father%2C%20grandfather%20and%20other%20blood%20relations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20had%20also%20submitted%20a%20pre-constitutional%20document%2C%20an%20extract%20of%20a%20book%2C%20in%20order%20to%20substantiate%20her%20claim%20of%20belonging%20to%20'Mahar'%2C%20which%20is%20a%20scheduled%20caste.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20said%20the%20committee%20had%20rendered%20the%20pre-constitutional%20document%20%26quot%3Botiose%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20more%20proof%20was%20required%20to%20be%20considered%20by%20the%20Committee%20who%20appears%20to%20have%20turned%20a%20Nelson's%20eye%20to%20this%20glaring%20document%20apart%20from%20three%20validity%20certificates%20which%20have%20already%20been%20granted%20by%20it%20in%20favour%20of%20blood%20relatives%20of%20the%20petitioner%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20high%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20quashed%20the%20scrutiny%20committee's%20order%20and%20directed%20it%20to%20issue%20a%20caste%20validity%20certificate%20to%20the%20petitioner%20as%20belonging%20to%20'Mahar'%20(Scheduled%20Caste)%20within%20a%20period%20of%20two%20weeks.%3Cbr%3E%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697701020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Falmiqti4_jesus-christ-picture-istock_625x300_19_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjesus-christs-picture-at-home-doesnt-mean-person-has-converted-to-christianity-high-court-4495111%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Merely%20having%20a%20picture%20of%20Jesus%20Christ%20in%20a%20house%20does%20not%20mean%20that%20a%20person%20has%20converted%20to%20Christianity%2C%20the%20Nagpur%20bench%20of%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20has%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjesus-christs-picture-at-home-doesnt-mean-person-has-converted-to-christianity-high-court-4495111%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjesus-chris