t%20the%20post-match%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20also%20the%20Netherlands'%20third%2050-over%20World%20Cup%20win%20and%20first%20in%2016%20years.%20They%20recorded%20their%20maiden%20victory%20against%20Namibia%20in%20the%202003%20edition%20in%20South%20Africa.%20Their%20second%20win%20was%20against%20Scotland%20in%20the%202007%20edition%20in%20the%20West%20Indies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENetherlands%20made%20it%20to%20the%20main%20tournament%20in%20India%20through%20the%20qualifying%20round%20and%20Edwards%20said%20his%20side%20did%20not%20come%20here%20just%20to%20make%20up%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYeah%2C%20absolutely.%20I%20think%20after%20qualifying%20we%20were%20pretty%20quick%20to%20set%20our%20minds%20to%20what%20we%20wanted%20to%20do%20at%20this%20tournament.%20We%20weren't%20coming%20here%20just%20to%20have%20fun%20and%20enjoy%20it.%20We're%20here%20to%20win%20games%20of%20cricket%20and%20give%20ourselves%20the%20best%20chance%20to%20make%20the%20next%20stage%2C%26quot%3B%20Edwards%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSouth%20Africa%20is%20obviously%20a%20very%20strong%20side%20and%20they'll%20be%20close%20to%20that%20semi-final%20spot.%20So%2C%20if%20we%20want%20to%20be%20amongst%20them%2C%20we've%20got%20to%20beat%20sides%20like%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%2027-year-old%20wicketkeeper.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20PTI%20inputs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697696640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fr6q87in_netherlands-celebration-afp_625x300_18_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fon-netherlands-little-guys-tag-ex-coach-gives-befitting-response-after-south-africa-triumph-4491782%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Victory%20against%20South%20Africa%20was%20Netherlands'%20third%20in%20the%20ODI%20format%20of%20the%20World%20Cup%20and%20first%20in%2016%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%