ir%20leaders%20may%20have%20different%20opinions%20in%20Kerala%20about%20the%20ongoing%20war%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%20over%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20group%20of%20people%20in%20a%20nondescript%20town%20in%20north%20Kerala%20have%20been%20diligently%20%26quot%3Bworking%26quot%3B%20for%20Israel%20before%20and%20after%20the%20deadly%20attack%20targeting%20civilians%20in%20that%20country%20by%20Hamas%20on%20October%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHundreds%20of%20tailors%20from%20a%20local%20apparel%20unit%20in%20Kannur%20have%20been%20working%20tirelessly%20to%20get%20the%20uniform%20shirts%20ready%20for%20the%20Israel%20police%20force%20for%20the%20past%20eight%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20politically%20volatile%20Kannur%20is%20also%20known%20for%20its%20glorious%20tradition%20of%20handloom%20making%20and%20textile%20export.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20tailors%20and%20employees%20at%20Maryan%20Apparel%20Pvt%20Limited%20in%20the%20district%20are%20behind%20the%20elegant%20light%20blue%2C%20long-sleeve%20uniform%20shirts%20of%20the%20Israel%20police%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENot%20just%20the%20double-pocket%20shirts%2C%20but%20the%20unit%20also%20designs%20and%20attaches%20the%20trademark%20emblems%20to%20its%20sleeves.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThomas%20Olickal%2C%20a%20Kerala%20businessman%20based%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20is%20the%20owner%20of%20the%20apparel%20unit%2C%20which%20currently%20employs%20over%201%2C500%20trained%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThomas%2C%20hailing%20from%20Thodupuzha%20in%20Idukki%20district%2C%20said%20the%20Israel%20police%20contacted%20the%20company%20even%20after%20the%20war%20began%20and%20placed%20additional%20orders%20for%20more%20uniforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20they%20placed%20an%20order%20for%20a%20new%20product%20from%20this%20year%20and%20the%20first%20shipment%20would%20be%20made%20by%20December.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20ordered%20for%20the%20cargo%20pants%20and%20shirt%20uniform%20set%20for%20their%20p