only%20if%20it%20was%20perfectly%20fit%20and%20the%20quality%20was%20up%20to%20par.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20wanted%20the%20ongoing%20war%20to%20end%20at%20the%20earliest%20and%20peace%20to%20return%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20war%20that%20began%20on%20October%207%20has%20become%20the%20deadliest%20of%20five%20Gaza%20wars%20for%20both%20sides.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Gaza%20Health%20Ministry%20said%202%2C778%20Palestinians%20have%20been%20killed%20and%209%2C700%20wounded.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnother%201%2C200%20people%20across%20Gaza%20are%20believed%20to%20be%20buried%20under%20the%20rubble%2C%20alive%20or%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMore%20than%201%2C400%20Israelis%20have%20been%20killed%2C%20and%20at%20least%20199%20others%2C%20including%20children%2C%20were%20captured%20by%20Hamas%20and%20taken%20into%20Gaza%2C%20according%20to%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697695680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F5d2n16k8_israel-police-afp_625x300_19_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthis-kerala-town-kannur-has-been-helping-israel-police-making-uniform-shirts-for-the-last-8-years-4494703%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Political%20parties%20and%20their%20leaders%20may%20have%20different%20opinions%20in%20Kerala%20about%20the%20ongoing%20war%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%20over%20Gaza.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A21%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthis-kerala-town-kannur-has-been-helping-israel-police-making-uniform-shirts-for-the-last-8-years-4494703%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthis-kerala-town-kannur-has-been-helping-israel-police-making-uniform-shirts-for