www.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fentertainment-arts-67145961%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fentertainment-arts-67145961.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fentertainment-arts-67145961.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Telangana%20Polls%3A%20BRS%20Has%20Reason%20Not%20To%20Be%20Overconfident%20With%20Congress%20Poised%20To%20Challenge%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18190018%2Fcollage-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EHyderabad%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20Five%20years%20can%20be%20a%20long%20time%2C%20especially%20in%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20thumping%20victory%20in%20the%20assembly%20elections%20in%20late%202018%2C%20the%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(BRS%2C%20then%20TRS)%20and%20K.%20Chandrashekar%20Rao%20(KCR)%E2%80%99s%20political%20dominance%20of%20Telangana%20seemed%20complete.%20But%20just%20months%20later%2C%20in%20the%202019%20general%20elections%2C%20the%20BRS%20managed%20to%20win%20just%20over%20half%20of%20the%2017%20seats%20on%20offer%20and%20both%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20and%20Congress%20performed%20much%20better%20than%20they%20did%20in%20the%20assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20subsequent%20years%2C%20all%20the%20parties%20have%20been%20through%20a%20roller-coaster%20of%20a%20ride.%20At%20one%20point%2C%20the%20BJP%20looked%20to%20be%20the%20BRS%E2%80%99s%20closest%20challenger.%20It%20has%20now%20retreated%20to%20a%20distant%20third.%20The%20Congress%2C%20having%20seen%2012%20of%20its%20MLAs%20defect%20to%20KCR%E2%80%99s%20party%20in%20the%20past%2C%20is%20now%20in%20pole%20position%20in%20the%20state%2C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.abplive.com%2Felections%2Ftelangana-election-opinion-poll-2023-abp-cvoter-survey-vote-seat-sharing-kaun-banega-mukhyamantri-bjp-congress-brs-dtp-1634722%5C%22%3E%20according%20to%20one%20opinion%20poll%3C%2Fa%3E.%20If%20that%20poll%20is%20to%20be%20believed%2C%20KCR%20%E2%80%93%20who%20might%20have%20hoped%20for%20a%20long%2C%20comfortable%20tenure%20in%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20chair%20like%20Odisha%E2%80%99s%20Naveen%20Patnaik%20%E2%80%93%20now%20has%20a%20fight%20on%20his%20hands%20to%20retain%20India%E2%80%99s%20youngest%20state%2C%20which%20goes%20to%20the%20polls%20on%20November%2030.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20the%20ground%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20Telangana%20was%20formed%20in%202014%2C%20the%20focus%20has%20been%20on%20the%20issues%20that%20were%20foregrounded%20in%20the%20movement%20for%20a%20separate%20state%3A%20creating%20jobs%3B%20providing%20irrigation%20facilities%20to%20the%20semi-arid%20region%E2%80%99s%20farmers%20and%20uplifting%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20marginalised%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKCR%20has%20initiated%20several%20development%20projects%20and%20welfare%20schemes%20in%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20and%20the%20BRS%E2%80%99s%20manifesto%20%E2%80%93%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Felections%2Ftelangana-assembly%2Fbrs-chief-kcr-releases-the-partys-manifesto-for-telangana-assembly-elections-2023%2Farticle67423344.ece%5C%22%3E%20released%20last%20Sunday%3C%2Fa%3E%20(October%2015)%20%E2%80%93%20promises%20to%20take%20this%20forward.%20From%20providing%20life%20insurance%20cover%20of%20Rs%205%20lakh%20to%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%2093%20lakh%20below%20poverty%20line%20(BPL)%20families%3B%20supplying%20superfine%20rice%20through%20the%20public%20distribution%20system%20to%20all%20ration%20card%20holders%3B%20and%20increasing%20the%20pensions%20for%20senior%20citizens%2C%20single%20women%20and%20disabled%20persons%2C%20the%20manifesto%20doubles%20down%20on%20the%20BRS%E2%80%99s%20core%20vision.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESuch%20programmes%2C%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20farmers%20and%20marginalised%20groups%2C%20were%20touted%20by%20KCR%20as%20the%20mantle%20for%20an%20%E2%80%9Calternative%20national%20agenda%E2%80%9D%20when%20he%20decided%20to%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fkcr-national-party-launch-soon%5C%22%3E%20take%20his%20party%20national%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20October%202022.%20But%20apart%20from%20opening%20an%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fhyderabad%2Ftelangana-cm-k-chandrasekhar-rao-inaugurates-brs-party-office-in-new-delhi%2Farticleshow%2F96221017.cms%5C%22%3E%20office%20in%20Delhi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20there%20has%20not%20been%20much%20progress%20on%20that%20front%20in%20the%20past%20year.%20The%20only%20party%20that%20publicly%20supported%20his%20national%20ambitions%20was%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20(Secular)%2C%20which%20has%20since%20joined%20the%20NDA.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMuch%20like%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20BRS%E2%80%99s%20organisational%20and%20decision-making%20structures%20are%20highly%20centralised.%20Though%20it%20has%20some%20leaders%20who%20command%20their%20own%20local%20following%2C%20it%20depends%20largely%20on%20the%20popularity%20of%20KCR%20and%20to%20a%20lesser%20extent%20his%20family%20members%20(son%20K.T.%20Rama%20Rao%20and%20nephew%20T.%20Harish%20Rao)%20during%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20anti-incumbency%20sentiment%20is%20more%20palpable%20this%20time%20around%20than%20it%20was%20five%20years%20ago%2C%20there%20is%20little%20doubt%20that%20KCR%20still%20enjoys%20the%20goodwill%20of%20a%20people%20who%20credit%20him%20for%20the%20formation%20of%20Telangana.%20This%20sentiment%20could%20prove%20crucial%20given%20that%20pollsters%20suggest%20the%20party%20is%20in%20a%20neck-and-neck%20fight%20with%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECongress%E2%80%99s%20change%20in%20fortunes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20Telangana%20unit%20has%20been%20re-energised%20by%20the%20party%20coming%20to%20power%20in%20neighbouring%20Karnataka.%20The%20grand%20old%20party%20has%20followed%20its%20now-familiar%20playbook%20in%20the%20state%20so%20far%2C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-unveils-six-guarantees-for-poll-bound-telangana-101694974676273.html%5C%22%3E%20making%20pre-poll%20guarantees%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20support%20women%2C%20farmers%2C%20housing%2C%20and%20financial%20assistance%20for%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Telangana%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20an%20exception%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20demand%20to%20hold%20a%20caste%20survey.%20In%20all%20the%20other%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fafter-bihar-cong-govt-in-rajasthan-to-conduct-caste-survey-makes-it-main-agenda-in-madhya-pradesh%5C%22%3E%20poll-bound%20states%3C%2Fa%3E%20(except%20Mizoram%2C%20where%20caste%20is%20not%20a%20factor)%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20promised%20to%20conduct%20a%20survey%20to%20reveal%20how%20much%20of%20the%20population%20is%20constituted%20of%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBCs)%2C%20Dalits%2C%20and%20tribal%20communities%2C%20and%20what%20is%20their%20share%20in%20decision-making.%20While%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20president%20wrote%20to%20KCR%20demanding%20a%20similar%20exercise%20in%20Telangana%2C%20it%20is%20unlikely%20to%20be%20the%20campaign%E2%80%99s%20tent-pole.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Telangana%2C%20the%20Congress%20is%20often%20referred%20to%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98Reddy%20party%E2%80%99%2C%20as%20it%20is%20dominated%20by%20leaders%20from%20the%20forward%20caste.%20Its%20first%20list%20of%20candidates%20for%20the%20assembly%20election%20also%20bears%20this%20out%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbctv18.com%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-assembly-election-2023-full-list-candidates-congress-party-18063161.htm%5C%22%3E15%20out%20of%20the%2055%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20Reddys.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20has%20already%20lost%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fhyderabad%2Fponnala-resigns-from-cong-over-raw-deal-to-bcs%2Farticleshow%2F104411985.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%20Ponnala%20Lakshmaiah%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20former%20minister%20in%20the%20undivided%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20state%2C%20for%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20sidelining%20of%20OBC%20leaders.%20He%20is%20likely%20to%20join%20the%20BRS.%20In%20such%20a%20scenario%2C%20posturing%20for%20a%20caste%20survey%20and%20promises%20to%20grant%20proportional%20representation%20may%20risk%20opening%20a%20Pandora%E2%80%99s%20box.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20necessity%20for%20a%20caste%20survey%20might%20also%20be%20negated%20by%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20KCR%20government%20in%202014%20conducted%20an%20extensive%20survey%20which%20collected%20not%20only%20caste-related%20but%20also%20other%20socio-economic%20data.%20It%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdata.telangana.gov.in%2Fdataset%2Fintegrated-household-survey%5C%22%3E%20showed%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20OBCs%20were%2053.5%25%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20population%2C%20while%20Dalits%20constituted%2018.5%25%20and%20(Scheduled%20Tribes)%20STs%2011.7%25.%20The%20general%20category%20(forward%20castes%2C%20some%20Muslims%2C%20and%20other%20religious%20minorities)%20was%20placed%20at%2016%25%20of%20the%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%20on%20the%20backfoot%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20will%20be%20disappointed%20with%20the%20downfall%20of%20its%20Telangana%20unit%20over%20the%20past%20year.%20After%20winning%20a%20series%20of%20bypolls%20and%20performing%20well%20in%20the%20Hyderabad%20municipal%20elections%2C%20the%20party%20seems%20to%20have%20lost%20focus%20and%20direction.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIts%20subdued%20mood%20is%20largely%20due%20to%20the%20removal%20of%20Bandi%20Sanjay%20as%20the%20state%20president%2C%20apparently%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Fnews-analysis%2Fstory%2Fbandi-sanjay-kishan-reddy-telangana-bjp-chief-forced-by-dissent-gets-makeover-2401787-2023-07-04%5C%22%3E%20under%20pressure%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20other%20senior%20leaders%20like%20Eatala%20Rajender.%20Sanjay%2C%20an%20MP%20from%20Karimnagar%2C%20was%20responsible%20for%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20growing%20footprint%20after%20having%20injected%20a%20brand%20of%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fbandi-sanjay-threatens-to-demolish-secretariat-domes-in-telangana-101676055868320.html%5C%22%3E%20aggressive%20communal%20rhetoric%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20was%2C%20so%20far%2C%20absent%20in%20the%20state.%20While%20Union%20minister%20G.%20Kishan%20Reddy%20has%20been%20roped%20in%20to%20replace%20him%2C%20the%20move%20spells%20damage%20control%20more%20than%20strategic%20reshuffle.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESanjay%E2%80%99s%20removal%20also%20highlights%20a%20problem%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20facing%20in%20several%20states%3A%20there%20is%20a%20vacuum%20of%20leaders%20who%20can%20work%20with%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20national%20leadership%20while%20also%20addressing%20state-level%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18190101%2FF8dw8AxbMAAAXBp-1.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22853%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18190101%2FF8dw8AxbMAAAXBp-1.jpeg%20853w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18190101%2FF8dw8AxbMAAAXBp-1-300x204.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-680709%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22579%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EBJP%20leader%20Bandi%20Sanjay.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40bandisanjay_bjp%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20the%20party%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fhyderabad%2Fpoll-pressure-bjp-directs-its-mps-mlas-to-contest-for-assembly%2Farticleshow%2F104270036.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%20may%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20as%20it%20has%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20%E2%80%9