-the-videos-tell-us-about-gaza-hospital-blast-sky-news-analysis-12987102%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fisrael-hamas-war-what-the-videos-tell-us-about-gaza-hospital-blast-sky-news-analysis-12987102%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%E2%80%99s%20Possible%20Olympic%20Bid%20Must%20Be%20for%20Sports%20Alone%2C%20Not%20Politics%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18180010%2FModi-at-IOC.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Last%20week%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20addressed%20the%20141st%20International%20Olympic%20Committee%20(IOC)%20session%20in%20Mumbai.%20During%20his%20speech%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Findia-will-bid-to-host-2036-olympics%5C%22%3Eexpressed%3C%2Fa%3E%20India%E2%80%99s%20interest%20in%20hosting%20the%20Olympics%2C%20stating%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20determination%20to%20prepare%20for%20the%202036%20event.%20He%20also%20mentioned%20India%E2%80%99s%20willingness%20to%20host%20the%202029%20Youth%20Olympics%2C%20expecting%20support%20from%20the%20IOC.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDespite%20India%E2%80%99s%20enthusiasm%2C%20the%20announcement%20of%20the%202036%20Olympic%20Summer%20Games%E2%80%99%20host%20will%20not%20take%20place%20before%202026%20or%202027.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20expected%20that%20the%20next%20Olympic%20Summer%20Games%20election%20will%20take%20place%20under%20the%20new%20IOC%20leadership%2C%20which%20would%20likely%20mean%20not%20before%202026%2F2027%2C%E2%80%9D%20an%20IOC%20spokesperson%20told%20%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20IOC%20session%20marked%20India%E2%80%99s%20second%20time%20as%20host.%20The%20first%20time%20was%20four%20decades%20ago%2C%20in%201983%20in%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20event%20this%20year%20was%20attended%20by%20global%20sports%20figures%2C%20including%20IOC%20president%20Thomas%20Bach.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20road%20to%20being%20the%20host%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20biggest%20sports%20event%20is%20not%20so%20simple.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20it%20possible%3F%20A%20varied%20scenario%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20of%20winning%20the%20bid%20to%20host%20the%20Olympic%20games%20is%20long.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20involves%20meticulous%20planning%2C%20strategic%20vision%20and%20rigorous%20evaluation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20timing%20of%20when%20the%20Olympic%20Games%20are%20awarded%20to%20a%20city%20varies%20significantly.%20Tokyo%20and%20Paris%20were%20named%20hosts%20seven%20years%20prior%20to%20the%20event%2C%20whereas%20Brisbane%20secured%20the%202032%20Games%20a%20staggering%2011%20years%20in%20advance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20any%20country%20to%20get%20approval%20to%20host%20the%20games%2C%20the%20country%20needs%20to%20pass%20a%20%E2%80%9Cfeasibility%20study%E2%80%9D%20conducted%20by%20the%20future%20host%20commission%20of%20the%20IOC%2C%20the%20panel%20responsible%20for%20identifying%20and%20recommending%20hosts%20of%20the%20Olympic%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18161615%2FInternational-Olympic-Committee-1024x448.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18161615%2FInternational-Olympic-Committee-1024x448.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18161615%2FInternational-Olympic-Committee-300x131.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18161615%2FInternational-Olympic-Committee.jpg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-680659%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22368%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EBased%20in%20Switzerland%2C%20the%20IOC%20is%20responsible%20for%20organising%20the%20summer%2C%20winter%20and%20youth%20Olympic%20games.%20Photo%3A%20Gzzz%2FWikimedia%20Commons.%20CC%20BY-SA%204.0.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20there%20are%20nearly%2020%20criteria%20based%20on%20which%20the%20IOC%20decides%20who%20the%20host%20would%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20reached%20out%20to%20former%20Croatia%20president%20and%20IOC%20member%20Kolinda%20Grabar-Kitarovic.%20She%20chairs%20the%20future%20host%20commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20reply%2C%20an%20IOC%20spokesperson%20said%20on%20her%20behalf%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20proposed%20masterplan%20of%20any%20interested%20party%20is%20considered%20by%20the%20future%20host%20commission%20during%20continuous%20dialogue%2C%20when%20the%20IOC%20conducts%20a%20feasibility%20study%20to%20help%20the%20interested%20party%20to%20improve%20its%20project%20and%20to%20assist%20the%20IOC%20executive%20board%20with%20its%20strategic%20long-term%20outlook%20and%20decision-making.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20IOC%20feasibility%20study%20examines%20the%20following%20criteria%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%A2%20Geopolitical%2C%20socio-economic%2C%20human%20development%20%26amp%3B%20environmental%20factors%3Cbr%3E%20%E2%80%A2%20Vision%20and%20venue%20masterplan%3Cbr%3E%20%E2%80%A2%20Alignment%20with%20existing%20long-term%20development%20plans%2C%20including%20youth%20strategies%3Cbr%3E%20%E2%80%A2%20Envisaged%20sustainability%20and%20legacy%20impacts%3Cbr%3E%20%E2%80%A2%20Political%20and%20public%20support%3Cbr%3E%20%E2%80%A2%20Funding%20strategy%3Cbr%3E%20%E2%80%A2%20Games%20delivery%20capabilities%20and%3Cbr%3E%20%E2%80%A2%20Sports%20event%20experience%2C%20accommodation%2C%20transport%2C%20safety%20and%20security%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20spokesperson%E2%80%99s%20reply%20continued%20to%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThough%20games%20are%20awarded%20to%20%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3Ecities%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20countries%20are%20often%20interested%20in%20them%20for%20reasons%20that%20go%20beyond%20sport.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOther%20than%20India%2C%20Mexico%2C%20Indonesia%20and%20Poland%20have%20officially%20expressed%20their%20interest%20in%20hosting%20the%202036%20Games.%20So%20not%20only%20is%20the%20competition%20fierce%2C%20there%20are%20questions%20on%20what%20is%20happening%20internally%20in%20sports%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMore%20medals%2C%20less%20money%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Youth%20Affairs%20and%20Sports%20has%20nearly%20doubled%20its%20budgetary%20allocation%20from%202014-15%20to%202023-24%2C%20reaching%20approximately%20Rs%203%2C400%20crores.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECentral%20to%20this%20effort%20is%20the%20Khelo%20India%20Scheme%2C%20which%20has%20received%20substantial%20financial%20support%2C%20playing%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20providing%20opportunities%20to%20around%2023%20lakh%20school%20children.%20Much%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20success%20at%20the%20Asian%20Games%20is%20being%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fopinion%2Fcolumns%2Fthe-secret-to-indias-asian-games-success-an-empowering-sports-policy-8978248%2F%5C%22%3Eattributed%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20this%20scheme%2C%20i.e.%20more%20money%2C%20more%20medals.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ugly%20Fans%20and%20Honourable%20Sportspersons%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fugly-fans-and-honourable-sportspersons%5C%22%3EUgly%20Fans%20and%20Honourable%20Sportspersons%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20won%20107%20medals%20at%20the%20recently%20concluded%20Asian%20Games%20in%20Guangzhou%2C%20beating%20its%20previous%20best%20of%2070%20medals%20in%20Jakarta%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20Neeraj%20Chopra%20acing%20every%20major%20competition%20since%20the%20Tokyo%20Olympics%2C%20and%20Indian%20sprinters%20%E2%80%93%20namely%20Muhammed%20Anas%20Yahiya%2C%20Amoj%20Jacob%2C%20Muhammed%20Ajmal%20Variyathodi%20and%20Rajesh%20Ramesh%20%E2%80%93%20winning%20gold%2C%20India%20has%20achieved%20unusual%20success%20in%20securing%20medals%20for%20track%20events.%20India%20has%20won%20a%20total%20of%2029%20medals%20in%20athletics.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20resurgence%20in%20shooting%2C%20marked%20by%20a%20remarkable%20haul%20of%2022%20medals%2C%20including%207%20golds%2C%20signifies%20a%20significant%20return%20to%20prominence%20in%20the%20shooting%20arena.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20end%20of%20the%20Asian%20Games%20has%20brought%20attention%20to%20significant%20disparities%20in%20both%20medal%20counts%20and%20government%20funding%20allocations%20among%20Indian%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGujarat%20failed%20to%20win%20a%20single%20medal%20at%20the%20Asian%20Games.%20It%20has%20to%20be%20pointed%20out%20that%20under%20the%20Khelo%20India%20scheme%2C%20it%20was%20sanctioned%20the%20highest%20funding%20of%20Rs%20608%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20having%2021%20medal%20winners%2C%20had%20secured%20the%20second-largest%20Khelo%20India%20funding%20of%20Rs%20503.02%20crore%2C%20Punjab%2C%20Maharashtra%20and%20Haryana%2C%20which%20collectively%20won%2075%20medals%2C%20were%20sanctioned%20less%20than%20Rs%20200%20crore%20combined%20from%20the%20Modi%20government%20under%20the%20Khelo%20India%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E(The%20three%20states%20were%20sanctioned%20Rs%2093%2C%20110%20and%2083%20crore%20respectively.)%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20there%20seems%20little%20connection%20between%20medals%20won%20and%C2%A0money%C2%A0allotted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20funding%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20220808155004%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2F164.100.24.220%2Floksabhaquestions%2Fannex%2F179%2FAU2614.pdf%5C%22%3Efigures%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20disclosed%20by%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Youth%20Affairs%20and%20Sports%20in%20August%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20discrepancy%20between%20Gujarat%E2%80%99s%20funding%20and%20its%20performance%2C%20coupled%20with%20the%20commendable%20achievements%20of%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20athletes%20with%20limited%20financial%20support%2C%20has%20sparked%20discussions%20about%20the%20need%20for%20a%20more%20transparent%20and%20equitable%20allocation%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fgaps-india-sports-administration-governance%5C%22%3EThe%20Gaps%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20Sports%20Administration%20and%20Governance%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnother%20persistent%20problem%20is%20the%20underutilisation%20of%20allocated%20resources%20and%20infrastructure.%20Despite%20the%20Khelo%20India%20scheme%20receiving%20Rs%20520%20crore%20and%20Rs%20500%20crore%20in%202018-19%20and%202019-20%2C%20the%20actual%20expenditure%20fell%20significantly%20short%2C%20standing%20at%20Rs%20324%20crore%20and%20Rs%20318%20crore%2C%20respectively%2C%20as%20noted%20by%20the%20Standing%20Committee%20on%20Human%20Resource%20Development%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20inefficient%20utilisation%20highlights%20graver%20problems%20than%20can%20be%20attended%20to%20by%20a%20mere%20upping%20of%20funds%20pumped%20in.%20They%20point%20to%20systemic%20challenges%20within%20India%E2%80%99s%20sports%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESports%20as%20a%20means%20for%20political%20PR%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20use%20of%20sports%20by%20politicians%20to%20gain%20political%20mileage%20is%20old%20news.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAdolf%20Hitler%20utilized%20the%201936%20Olympics%20hosted%20in%20Berlin%20to%20reshape%20the%20image%20of%20Nazi%20Germany.%20Hitler%20and%20Nazi%20officials%20skillfully%20tried%20to%20use%20the%20Olympics%20to%20push%20for%20large%20crowds%20in%20adulation%20of%20Der%20Fuhrer%20and%20the%20idea%20of%20German%20supremacy%20which%20the%20Nazis%20believed%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20time%20when%20Nazi%20Germany%20faced%20international%20criticism%2C%20the%20Olympics%20also%20provided%20the%20perfect%20opportunity%20for%20Hitler%20to%20charm%20global%20counterparts%20and%20portray%20the%20nation%20as%20open-minded%20and%20welcoming.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENoted%20journalist%20and%20author%20Eduardo%20Galeano%2C%20in%20his%20book%20%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3ESoccer%20in%20Sun%20and%20Shadow%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20writes%20how%20%E2%80%9Cthe%201934%20World%20Cup%20in%20Rome%20was%20an%20elaborate%20propaganda%20operation.%20Mussolini%20attended%20every%20match%2C%20sitting%20in%20the%20box%20of%20honor%2C%20his%20chin%20raised%20toward%20stands%20filled%20with%20black%20shirts.%20The%20eleven%20players%20of%20the%20Italian%20squad%20dedicated%20their%20victories%20to%20him%2C%20their%20right%20arms%20outstretched.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPoliticians%20of%20the%20current%20age%20have%20successfully%20used%20sports%20events%20for%20their%20own%20image-building.%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20ride%20in%20a%20%E2%80%98chariot%E2%80%99%20around%20the%20stadium%20named%20after%20him%20in%20Ahmedabad%20with%20Australian%20PM%20Anthony%20Albanese%20got%20panned%20and%20was%20called%20out%20for%20the%20use%20of%20sports%20to%20enhance%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F3fdrQrjAO4w%3Fsi%3Dyr5MF8X6MKO4uNWO%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20sports%20writer%20Gideon%20Haigh%20%E2%80%93%20who%20was%20there%20in%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20stadium%20when%20the%20two%20PMs%20wheeled%20about%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVKStVlWdhuQ%5C%22%3Espoke%20of%20the%20India-Pakistan%20match%20at%20the%20same%20venue%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20sight%20of%20all%20those%20blue%20shirts%20at%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20stadium%20the%20other%20night%20was%20bizarre.%20It%20looked%20like%20a%20Nuremberg%20rally%2C%20didn%E2%80%99t%20it%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhich%20city%3F%20Ahmedabad%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20significant%20step%20towards%20a%20possible%20bid%20to%20host%20the%202036%20Olympics%2C%20the%20Ahmedabad%20Urban%20Development%20Authority%20(AUDA)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fahmedabad%2Folympic-village-sardar-patel-sports-enclave-to-now-cover-650-acres%2Farticleshow%2F102665722.cms%5C%22%3Ehas%20earmarked%20an%20additional%2050%20acres%20of%20land%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20part%20of%20the%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20expansive%20initiative%20to%20establish%20cutting-edge%20sports%20facilities%20in%20and%20around%20Ahmedabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20ambitious%20project%20aims%20to%20create%20the%20Sardar%20Patel%20Sports%20Enclave%20and%20the%20Olympic%20Village%2C%20pivotal%20components%20for%20hosting%20the%20global%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20cricket%20World%20Cup%20is%20hosted%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20home%20turf%2C%20there%20is%20speculation%20that%20it%20conveniently%20coincides%20with%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20re-election%20campaign%20months%20before%20the%20general%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20BCCI%20under%20Jay%20Shah%20%E2%80%93%20coincidentally%2C%20the%20son%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20home%20minister%2C%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20seen%20as%20the%20second-most%20powerful%20Indian%20today%20after%20Modi%20%E2%80%93%20now%20wields%20considerable%20influence%20on%20the%20world%20cricket%20calendar.%20This%20was%20evident%20when%20matches%20moved%20from%20Pakistan%20to%20Sri%20Lanka%20due%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20refusal%20to%20travel%20there%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20IOC%20member%20Kolinda%20Grabar-Kitarovic%20highlighted%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20increasing%20politicisation%20of%20sports%20in%20an%20update%20to%20international%20sports%20officials%20regarding%20nations%20aspiring%20to%20host%20future%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReplying%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20query%2C%20an%20IOC%20spokesperson%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Ccommitting%20to%20respect%20the%20Olympic%20charter%20means%20committing%20to%20preserve%20the%20practice%20of%20sport%20as%20a%20human%20right%20and%20the%20practice%20of%20political%20neutrality%20in%20sport.%20This%20includes%20letting%20athletes%20from%20all%20parts%20in%20the%20world%20come%20into%20your%20country%20to%20participate.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Pakistan's%20Cricket%20Team%20in%20India%3A%20Why%20Discourtesy%20Is%20Not%20Diplomacy%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Findia-pakistan-world-cup-cricket%5C%22%3EPakistan%E2%80%99s%20Cricket%20Team%20in%20India%3A%20Why%20Discourtesy%20Is%20Not%20Diplomacy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSports%20organisations%20including%20NOCs%20%5BNational%20Olympic%20Committees%5D%20have%20the%20right%20and%20the%20obligation%20to%20operate%20without%20political%20interference%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20IOC%20spokesperson%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20intersection%20of%20sport%20and%20politics%2C%20while%20natural%2C%20also%20makes%20all%20%E2%80%98sporting%20decisions%E2%80%99%20merit%20scrutiny.%20While%20sports%20brings%20joy%20to%20fans%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20disconcerting%20to%20acknowledge%20that%20this%20happiness%20often%20stems%20from%20morally%20questionable%20endeavors.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2022%2Fnov%2F11%2Fengland-supporter-conflicted-over-qatar-world-cup-human-rights-record-gay-rights-boycott-tournament%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20in%20a%20recent%20editorial%20on%20%E2%80%98sportswashing%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20writes%20of%20India%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%20and%20more%20countries%20it%20claims%20are%20trying%20to%20use%20sports%20in%20ways%20that%20may%20not%20be%20very%20sportsmanlike.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CRealpolitik%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20overlooked.%20Respecting%20different%20cultures%20does%20not%20mean%20abuse%20is%20condoned.%20The%20lure%20of%20the%20arena%20ought%20not%20excuse%20a%20lack%20of%C2%A0moral%C2%A0responsibility.%20Sport%20can%20produce%20great%20public%20happiness%2C%20and%20the%20idea%20that%20only%20the%20ill-intentioned%20would%20censure%20it.%20But%20it%20jars%20to%20know%20that%20the%20pure%20joy%20experienced%20by%20many%20fans%20rests%20on%20the%20fruits%20of%20baseness.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20well%20be%20an%20Indian%20dream%20to%20be%20the%20host%20of%20the%20Olympic%20Games%2C%20but%20this%20dream%20must%20come%20only%20for%20sports%20and%20not%20for%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697641821000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18180010%2FModi-at-IOC.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Findias-possible-olympic-bid-must-be-for-sports-alone-not-politics%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20history%20of%20sports%20%E2%80%93%20for%20example%2C%20the%20Berlin%20Olympics%20in%201936%2C%20the%20Saudi%20Arabian%20drive%20to%20host%20the%20prestigious%20World%20Golfing%20tournament%20and%20the%20purchase%20of%20European%20Football%20clubs%20%E2%80%93%20drives%20the%20fear%20of%20%E2%80%98sportswashing%E2%80%99.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Findias-possible-olympic-bid-must-be-for-sports-alone-not-politics%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20to%20Raise%20Politically%20Aware%20Children%20in%20India%3F%20Study%20Shares%20Guide%20for%20Parents%20%26amp%3B%20Teachers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%8B%E2%80%8BGrowing%20up%20as%20a%20young%20girl%20in%20Mumbai%20in%20the%201990s%2C%20nobody%20spoke%20to%20me%20about%20politics%20nor%20did%20I%20have%20a%20safe%20space%20to%20ask%20questions%20or%20discuss%20policy%20issues.%20Unlike%20adolescents%20today%2C%20we%20did%20not%20have%20access%20to%20the%20internet%20or%20social%20media.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMy%20journey%20towards%20political%20awareness%20started%20in%20my%20early%2020s%20and%20I%20only%20wish%20it%20had%20started%20earlier.%20I%20started%20thinking%20a%20lot%20about%20how%20women%20were%20represented%20in%20politics%20when%20I%20had%20the%20opportunity%20to%20work%20closely%20with%20the%20Delhi%20government%20in%202018.%20I%20saw%20only%20a%20handful%20of%20women%20around%20me%2C%20but%20the%20ones%20that%20I%20did%20see%20were%20extremely%20inspiring.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20we%20want%20to%20bridge%20the%20gender%20gap%20in%20politics%2C%20I%20believe%20that%20it%20is%20important%20to%20create%20a%20safe%20environment%20for%20young%20girls%20to%20have%20political%20discourse.%20They%20also%20need%20to%20have%20access%20to%20neutral%20political%20information%2C%20and%20with%20that%20goal%20in%20mind%2C%20I%20started%20to%20research%20women%E2%80%99s%20representation%20in%20Indian%20electoral%20politics%20and%20began%20our%20work%20at%20Kuviraa.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKuviraa%20is%20a%20nonpartisan%20initiative%20that%20works%20to%20build%20political%20leadership%20and%20civic%20action%20in%20adolescent%20girls%20across%20India.%20Our%20goal%20is%20to%20make%20politics%20accessible%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F235373%2Findia-youth-young-inspiring-heroes-international-youth-day-innovation-bravery-courage-ros174%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eyoung%20people%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20create%20spaces%20for%20dialogue.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20wanted%20to%20understand%20what%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F160414%2Fanudip-foundation-youth-skilling%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eyoung%20Indian%20%3C%2Fa%3Egirls%20thought%20of%20politics%20and%20if%20they%20were%20even%20interested%20in%20getting%20involved.%20Although%20there%20was%20some%20research%20done%20in%20the%20global%20context%2C%20we%20found%20no%20data%20on%20political%20interest%20or%20engagement%20among%20Indian%20adolescents%20to%20start%20off%20with.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThrough%20interviews%20with%20adolescent%20girls%2C%20parents%20and%20school%20leaders%2C%20we%20learnt%20that%20politics%20was%20not%20an%20aspirational%20career%20choice%20for%20many%20in%20India%20because%20of%20the%20stigma%20attached%20to%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20found%20that%20schools%20and%20parents%20were%20even%20reluctant%20to%20speak%20to%20their%20children%20about%20politics.%20Some%20teachers%20whom%20we%20interviewed%20told%20us%20that%20we%20were%20welcome%20to%20speak%20to%20the%20students%20about%20policies%20but%20not%20politics%20as%20it%20could%20be%20divisive.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20improve%20political%20representation%20and%20engagement%2C%20we%20need%20to%20spark%20political%20interest%20and%20civic%20action%20at%20a%20young%20age.%20For%20this%2C%20we%20wanted%20to%20understand%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20problem%20and%20decided%20to%20conduct%20a%20study%20with%20researchers%20from%20the%C2%A0%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fluskin.ucla.edu%2Fsocial-welfare%5C%22%3EUniversity%20of%20California%2C%20Los%20Angeles%E2%80%99%20Department%20of%20Social%20Welfare%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESara%20Wilf%2C%20the%20lead%20researcher%20on%20this%20study%2C%20explains%20how%20the%20study%20aims%20to%20fill%20the%20knowledge%20gap%20between%20gender%20disparities%20in%20political%20interest%20and%20engagement%20across%20adolescence%20and%20young%20adulthood%20in%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20thrilled%20to%20work%20on%20this%20research%20with%20Kuviraa%20and%20their%20brilliant%20volunteers%20who%20care%20so%20deeply%20about%20this%20issue.%20I%E2%80%99m%20excited%20that%20this%20study%20both%20gives%20practical%20recommendations%20for%20parents%20and%20educators%20to%20increase%20female%20political%20engagement%2C%20and%20identifies%20many%20pathways%20for%20future%20research%20into%20a%20topic%20that%20is%20critical%20for%20equity%20and%20democracy%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sara%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EKey%20research%20findings%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EOur%20report%20%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kuviraa.org%2F_files%2Fugd%2F4457e5_dbf1d4b8dde54864ab517d0334954c45.pdf%5C%22%3ETalk%20Politics%20to%20Me%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eunpacks%20the%20concept%20of%20Gendered%20Political%20Socialisation%2C%20which%20sheds%20light%20on%20the%20complexities%20of%20gender%20disparities%20in%20political%20interest%20and%20its%20influence%20by%20factors%20such%20as%20family%2C%20social%20media%20and%20news%2C%20among%20other%20important%20insights.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20mother%20of%20a%2014-year-old%20girl%20from%20New%20Delhi%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20avoid%20discussing%20politics%20with%20her%20because%20of%20how%20badly%20it%20is%20covered%20in%20the%20news%20and%20its%20tendency%20to%20address%20issues%20through%20the%20lens%20of%20social%20justice.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMany%20girls%20may%20encounter%20perceived%20limitations%20in%20their%20political%20aspirations%20due%20to%20gender%20stereotypes%20and%20societal%20expectations.%20Conversely%2C%20boys%20may%20be%20encouraged%20or%20empowered%20to%20take%20risks%2C%20leadership%20roles%20and%20engage%20more%20actively%20in%20politics.%20Addressing%20such%20influences%20at%20an%20early%20age%20is%20crucial%20to%20foster%20inclusive%20political%20participation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20had%20a%20school%20trustee%20from%20Chennai%20tell%20us%20that%20a%20class%2010%20student%20from%20their%20school%20aspired%20to%20be%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20New%20Zealand%20as%20she%20saw%20Jacinda%20Adern%20as%20a%20role%20model.%20I%20thought%20it%20was%20extremely%20sad%20that%20young%20girls%20in%20our%20country%20think%20it%20is%20more%20achievable%20to%20become%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20in%20a%20country%20other%20than%20their%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%2016-year-old%20girl%20who%20took%20our%20survey%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CDue%20to%20the%20misconception%20that%20only%20men%20can%20be%20politicians%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20women%20don%E2%80%99t%20put%20a%20thought%20into%20becoming%20a%20politician.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnother%2017-year-old%20female%20respondent%20to%20our%20survey%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CGetting%20nominated%20by%20one%E2%80%99s%20own%20party%20members%20itself%20is%20difficult%20to%20begin%20with%20for%20a%20woman%20due%20to%20the%20general%20preconceived%20notion%20that%20a%20man%20does%20the%20job%20better%20without%20any%20emotional%20connect.%20People%20trust%20a%20man%20more%20than%20a%20woman%20in%20a%20position%20of%20power%20and%20they%20believe%20that%20a%20woman%20isn%E2%80%99t%20mentally%20strong%20enough%20to%20tackle%20issues%20and%20work%20on%20par%20with%20her%20male%20counterparts.%20Hence%2C%20even%20if%20nominated%2C%20getting%20the%20public%20to%20vote%20for%20a%20woman%20is%20difficult%20because%20of%20their%20low%20trust%20in%20a%20female%20figure%20of%20authority%20due%20to%20their%20stereotypical%20views%20and%20an%20inherently%20patriarchal%20mindset.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%2017-year-old%20male%20respondent%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20more%20difficult%20for%20female%20politicians%20to%20be%20successful%20since%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20get%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F69190%2Fyouth-india-org-social-activism-online%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eequal%20opportunities%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20men%20and%20even%20if%20they%20were%20to%20be%20on%20the%20same%20platform%2C%20Indians%2C%20including%20women%20themselves%2C%20have%20a%20tendency%20to%20look%20at%20them%20as%20%E2%80%9Cinferior%E2%80%9D%20or%20%E2%80%9Cweak%E2%80%9D%20compared%20to%20men.%E2%80%9D%20This%20sentiment%20was%20also%20echoed%20by%20another%2018-year-old%20male%20participant%20of%20the%20survey.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20interesting%20part%20of%20the%20study%20was%20that%20our%20team%20of%20research%20volunteers%20consisted%20of%20young%20girls%20and%20women%20between%20ages%2015-%2021%2C%20who%20worked%20on%20the%20analysis%20of%20open-ended%20responses.%20This%20helped%20us%20identify%20trends%20in%20the%20responses%20of%20their%20peers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20India%20gears%20up%20for%20a%20general%20election%20in%202024%2C%20educators%2C%20the%20civil%20society%20and%20philanthropists%20must%20come%20together%20to%20create%20an%20enabling%20environment%20for%20future%20and%20first-time%20voters%20as%20we%20cannot%20have%20a%20truly%20functional%20democracy%20without%20the%20youths%E2%80%99%20participation%20and%20engagement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FGender-Disparity-Politics-Infographic-1-1697633742.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FGender-Disparity-Politics-Infographic-1-1697633742.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FGender-Disparity-Politics-Infographic-1-1697633742-300x153.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FGender-Disparity-Politics-Infographic-1-1697633742-500x255.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FGender-Disparity-Politics-Infographic-1-1697633742-768x392.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FGender-Disparity-Politics-Infographic-1-1697633742-150x77.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332517%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22612%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERecommendations%20for%20parents%20and%20caregivers%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20a%20few%20recommendations%20for%20what%20parents%2C%20schools%20and%20caregivers%20can%20do%20to%20increase%20political%20interest%20and%20engagement%20among%20adolescents%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Col%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ECreate%20safe%20spaces%20for%20dialogue%20on%20politics%20at%20home%20and%20school%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe%20found%20that%20youth%20had%20higher%20political%20engagement%20if%20their%20parents%20encouraged%20them%20to%20participate%20in%20politics.%20Young%20men%20are%20more%20likely%20than%20young%20women%20to%20be%20socialised%20by%20their%20parents%20and%20society%20to%20think%20about%20politics%20as%20a%20career%20path%20which%20may%20be%20one%20reason%20we%20see%20a%20lower%20political%20participation%20of%20women%20beyond%20voting.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3EWe%20interviewed%20a%20father%20of%20a%2015-year-old%20girl%20from%20Mumbai%20who%20said%20that%20he%20uses%20events%20that%20change%20the%20course%20of%20the%20world%20to%20discuss%20political%20issues%20and%20takes%20opposing%20views%20than%20his%20daughter%20to%20encourage%20her%20to%20read%20more%20so%20she%20can%20form%20a%20strong%20argument%20against%20him.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3EHajer%20Sharief%2C%20a%20Libyan%20peace%20and%20human%20rights%20activist%2C%20introduces%20a%20simple%20yet%20transformative%20idea%20%E2%80%93%20parents%20can%20teach%20their%20children%20about%20political%20functioning%20by%20giving%20them%20a%20say%20in%20how%20their%20households%20are%20run%2C%20in%20the%20form%20of%20regular%20family%20meetings%20where%20everyone%20has%20an%20equal%20say%20and%20learns%20to%20negotiate%20their%20demands%20and%20put%20across%20their%20feelings.%20This%20way%20young%20people%2C%20both%20boys%20and%20girls%2C%20learn%20similar%20skills%20and%20have%20the%20same%20space%20to%20discuss%20and%20deliberate.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Fol%3E%20%3Col%20start%3D%5C%222%5C%22%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ECreate%20structured%20opportunities%20for%20girls%20to%20lead%20and%20highlight%20women%20politicians%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESchools%20play%20an%20important%20role%20in%20supporting%20the%20political%20development%20of%20young%20children%20and%20through%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F13819%2Funleash-dreams-india-youth-loan-vocational-training-skills-milaap%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esuch%20activities%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20can%20increase%20their%20interest%20in%20civic%20action.%20%E2%80%98Action%20civics%E2%80%99%2C%20where%20students%20learn%20important%20civic%20skills%20and%20then%20lead%20their%20own%20initiatives%2C%20has%20been%20shown%20to%20increase%20a%20student%E2%80%99s%20sense%20of%20civic%20competence%20and%20agency%20(LeCompte%20et%20al.%2C%202020).%C2%A0%3Cbr%3EKuviraa%E2%80%99s%20flagship%20%E2%80%98Ambassador%20Program%E2%80%99%20gives%20girls%20an%20opportunity%20to%20participate%20in%20mock%20elections%20through%20a%20campaign%20simulation%20exercise%20and%20creates%20a%20platform%20for%20them%20to%20interact%20with%20women%20political%20and%20civic%20leaders%20across%20parties%20and%20government%20levels.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Fol%3E%20%3Col%20start%3D%5C%223%5C%22%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EIdentify%20structural%20sexism%20and%20how%20it%20impacts%20all%20genders%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Structural%20sexism%20and%20gender%20stereotypes%20can%20influence%20young%20minds%20into%20thinking%20that%20certain%20fields%20are%20only%20for%20men%20or%20that%20women%20cannot%20be%20good%20leaders.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3EDr%20Emily%20Setty%2C%20who%20has%20conducted%