0party%2C%20NISHAD%20party%2C%20Apna%20Dal%2C%20Hindustani%20Awam%20Morcha%20(Secular)%2C%20PMK%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20Jharkhand%E2%80%99s%20AJSU-P.%20In%20the%20next%20few%20weeks%2C%20we%20will%20know%20the%20full%20impact%20of%20Nitish%E2%80%99s%20bombshell.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20alliance%20with%20Karnataka%E2%80%99s%20JD(S)%2C%20which%20has%20been%20in%20a%20frantic%20search%20for%20partners%2C%20has%20been%20a%20significant%20gain%20for%20the%20BJP.%20However%2C%20the%20crucial%20issue%20of%20seat%20adjustment%20remains%20a%20problem.%20The%20understanding%20with%20the%20BJP%20has%20already%20triggered%20rumbling%20among%20ticket%20aspirants.%20Several%20senior%20leaders%2C%20especially%20from%20minority%20communities%2C%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fbengaluru-news%2Fjds-holds-meeting-amid-rumblings-over-bjp-tieup-101696190105932.html%5C%22%3Equit%20in%20protest%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20week%2C%20the%20JD(S)%20Karnataka%20chief%2C%20CM%20Ibrahim%20said%20that%20the%20party%20will%20not%20ally%20with%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EBut%20the%20biggest%20blow%20to%20the%20BJP%20came%20from%20its%20long-time%20ally%20AIADMK%2C%20which%20has%20%E2%80%98finally%E2%80%99%20decided%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thequint.com%2Fsouth-india%2Fannamalai-aiadmk-bjp-snapping-ties-dravidian-politics-tamil-nadu%5C%22%3Esnap%20ties%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20BJP%20was%20expecting%20as%20many%20as%20six%20seats%20from%20Tamil%20Nadu%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20AIADMK%E2%80%99s%20own%20tally.%20Among%20the%20reasons%20cited%20for%20the%20breakup%20was%20minority%20votes.%20The%20BJP%20is%20trying%20hard%20for%20a%20patch-up%2C%20but%20so%20far%20the%20latter%20has%20brushed%20these%20efforts%20aside.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20BJP%20had%20made%20considerable%20headway%20in%20its%20outreach%20programme%2C%20especially%20with%20Pasmandas.%20Last%20year%2C