as%20been%20the%20most%20isolated%20and%20the%20best%20thing%20one%20can%20do%20is%20listen.%20If%20a%20person%20needs%20professional%20help%2C%20we%20refer%20them%20to%20our%20psychologists%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Raj.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98A%20dark%20pit%20that%20can%20swallow%20you%20whole%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20in%20a%20happy%20family%2C%20Raj%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331526%2Fpune-startup-innovates-ai-based-technology-screen-tuberculosis-within-seconds-innovation-in-healthcare%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emoved%20to%20Pune%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20his%20engineering%20course.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20when%20I%20was%20in%20Pune%20when%20things%20started%20to%20go%20downhill.%20I%20was%20in%20a%20relationship%20with%20a%20person%20and%20it%20did%20not%20work%20out.%20I%20was%20not%20doing%20good%20at%20college%20either.%20Suddenly%2C%20life%20felt%20hard%20and%20I%20felt%20alone%20in%20all%20of%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls%20adding%20that%20he%20felt%20helpless.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fraj-dagwar-1-1697611896.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Raj%20suffered%20from%20depression%20for%20about%20seven%20months%20before%20getting%20help%20from%20a%20college%20therapist.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fraj-dagwar-1-1697611896.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fraj-dagwar-1-1697611896-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fraj-dagwar-1-1697611896-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%